as%20to%20take%20collective%20action%20whether%20it%20is%20crypto%2C%20global%20debt%2C%20etc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EI%20will%20completely%20credit%20the%20success%20of%20the%20G20%20Summit%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20for%20having%20a%20complete%20picture%2C%20much%20before%20we%20started%2C%20about%20India's%20stature%2C%20India's%20image.%20The%20vision%20of%20the%20PM%20played%20out%20and%20it%20benefitted%20all.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20Delhi%20Declaration%20has%20set%20India%20in%20a%20different%20class%20altogether.%20We%20have%20proven%20that%20we%20can%20be%20a%20force%20for%20bringing%20people%20together%20even%20on%20very%20divisive%20issues%20and%20be%20a%20beacon%20of%20hope.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20maturity%20with%20which%20Indian%20negotiating%20teams%20handled%20it%20at%20every%20stage%20was%20%26quot%3Bcraftsmanship%26quot%3B.%20Remarkably%2C%20my%20G20%20team%20was%20largely%20made%20up%20of%20women%20who%20led%20from%20the%20front.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20India's%20Digital%20Payments%20Infrastructure%20(DPI)%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20interest%20in%20DPI.%20The%20way%20India%20has%20used%20digital%20infrastructure%20has%20earned%20praise%20from%20global%20leaders%2C%20including%20the%20World%20Bank.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20the%20Indian%20rupee%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Around%2022%20countries%20are%20approaching%20us%20to%20know%20if%20bilateral%20talks%20can%20be%20done%20over%20the%20Indian%20rupee.%20Many%20countries%20are%20running%20short%20on%20their%20dollar%20reserve.%20They%20are%20seeing%20the%20Indian%20rupee%20as%20a%20stable%20currency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20Sanatana%20Dharma%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20have%20lived%20experiences%20of%20what%20the%20DMK%20is%20talking%20about.%20Anti-Hindu%2C%20anti-Sanatana%2C%20and%20anti-caste%20are%20the%20pronounced%20policies%20of%20the%20DMK%2C%20and%20they%20execute%20them%20relentlessly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20DMK%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20people%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20have%20suffered.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20country%20did%20not%20understand%20because%20of%20a%20language%20barrier.%20It%20has%20always%20been%20like%20that.%20Now%20because%20of%20social%20media%2C%20you%20do%20not%20even%20need%20a%20translator%20to%20know%20what%20a%20minister%20is%20saying.%20It%20is%20not%20surprising.%20DMK%20has%20been%20doing%20it%20for%2070%20years.%20It%20is%20hypocrisy.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20Opposition%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%20against%20Sanatana%20Dharma.%20The%20government%20is%20willing%20to%20engage%20with%20opposition%20parties%20with%20facts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20caste%20census%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20am%20not%20going%20to%20comment.%20Different%20states%20are%20projecting%20it%20differently.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694761020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Ffa86ojbg_nirmala-sitharaman_625x300_15_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-willing-to-engage-with-india-bloc-over-facts-nirmala-sitharamans-top-quotes-4391917%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20G20%2C%20Sanatana%20Dharma%2C%20and%20INDIA%20bloc%20-%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20spoke%20about%20India's%20grand%20success%20in%20hosting%20a%20global%20event%20and%20slammed%20the%20Opposition%20over%20DMK%20leader%20Udhayanidhi%20Stalin's%20remarks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-willing-to-engage-with-india-bloc-over-facts-nirmala-sitharamans-top-quotes-4391917%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20Why%20Pakistan%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20Both%20Scored%20252%2C%20Yet%20Babar's%20Team%20Lost%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Asia%20Cup%202023%20Super%204%20match%20between%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20Pakistan%20went%20down%20the%20wire%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Dasun%20Shanaka%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F59545-madagamagamage-dasun-shanaka-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDasun%20Shanaka%3C%2Fa%3E's%20men%20securing%20the%20victory%20on%20the%20last%20ball%20of%20the%20match.%20Sri%20Lanka%20were%20given%20a%20target%20of%20252%20runs%20to%20chase%20by%20Pakistan%20after%20rain%20reduced%20the%20match%20to%2042%20overs%20per%20side.%20However%2C%20confusion%20with%20regards%20to%20the%20match%20has%20got%20fans%20scratching%20their%20heads%2C%20as%20both%20Pakistan%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20managed%20to%20put%20252%20runs%20on%20the%20board.%20Yet%2C%20the%20match%20went%20in%20the%20favour%20of%20the%20islanders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBatting%20first%2C%20Pakistan%20put%20252%20runs%20on%20he%20board%20for%20the%20loss%20of%207%20wickets%20in%2042%20overs.%20But%2C%20initially%2C%20the%20match%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20a%2045%20overs%20per%20side%20contest.%20It%20first%20started%20raining%20at%20the%20R%20Premadasa%20Stadium%20in%20Colombo%20before%20the%20match%20started%2C%20delaying%20the%20toss%20and%20the%20start%20of%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20match%20first%20started%2C%20it%20was%20announced%20that%20each%20team%20would%20bat%20for%2045%20overs.%20But%2C%20rain%20came%20pouring%20again%2C%20prompting%20the%20authorities%20to%20reduce%20the%20match%20further%20to%2042%20over%20for%20each%20team.%20Pakistan%20were%20batting%20on%20130%2F5%20in%2027.4%20overs%20when%20the%20rain%20came%20pouring%20for%20the%20second%20time%2C%20making%20the%20match%20a%2042-over%20contest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Pakistan's%20Revised%20Total%20was%20251%20runs%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Pakistan%20put%20252%20runs%20on%20the%20board%20in%2042%20overs%2C%201%20run%20was%20deducted%20from%20the%20kitty%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Duckworth-Lewis%20calculation.%20The%20deduction%20happened%20because%20Pakistan%20had%20lost%205%20wickets%20before%20the%20second%20rain%20delay%20in%20the%20match.%20Hence%2C%20the%20final%20total%20came%20out%20to%20be%20251%20runs%2C%20with%20Sri%20Lanka%20now%20needing%20252%20runs%20to%20win%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20has%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20had%20Pakistan%20not%20lost%20the%20wicket%20of%20Mohammad%20Nawaz%20right%20before%20the%20rain%20delay%20in%20the%2028th%20over%2C%20Sri%20Lanka's%20target%20would've%20been%20255%20runs%20instead%20of%20252.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20DLS%20calculations%2C%20keeping%20wickets%20in%20hand%20is%20crucial%20for%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhenever%20it%20comes%20to%20rain-affected%20matches%2C%20getting%20off%20to%20a%20good%20start%20becomes%20quite%20important%20for%20teams.%20Losing%20early%20wickets%20often%20hurts%20the%20teams'%20chances%20of%20getting%20a%20better%20revised%20total%20even%20if%20they%20improve%20in%20the%20later%20stages%20of%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20was%20the%20scenario%20for%20Pakistan%20as%20Sri%20Lanka%20held%20on%20to%20their%20nerves%20in%20the%20death%20overs%20to%20take%20the%20team%20into%20the%20final.%20Needing%206%20runs%20from%20the%20final%202%20balls%2C%20batting%20all-rounder%20Charith%20Asalanka%20hit%20the%20winning%20runs%20for%20his%20team%20and%20set%20up%20the%20Asia%20Cup%202023%20final%20clash%20against%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694760600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fsvpmkd7o_babar-azam-team-afp_625x300_15_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fexplained-how-pakistan-sri-lanka-both-scored-252-yet-babar-azams-men-lost-asia-cup-match-4391864%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan%20scored%20252%2F7%20in%2042%20overs%20while%20Sri%20Lanka%20scored%20252%2F8%20in%20the%20same%20number%20of%20overs.%20Yet%2C%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20team%20won%20the%20match.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fexplained-how-pakistan-sri-lanka-both-scored-252-yet-babar-azams-men-lost-asia-cup-match-4391864%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fexplained-how-pakistan-sri-lanka-both-scored-252-yet-babar-azams-men-lost-asia-cup-match-4391864%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Fexplained-how-pakistan-sri-lanka-both-scored-252-yet-babar-azams-men-lost-asia-cup-match-4391864%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Anurag%20says%20Ranveer%20wanted%20to%20do%20Bombay%20Velvet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694760420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103683489%2Cimgsize-23884.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fanurag-kashyap-says-ranveer-singh-really-wanted-to-do-bombay-velvet-reveals-why-ranbir-kapoor-replaced-him%2Farticleshow%2F103683489.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103683489.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAnurag%20Kashyap%20revealed%20that%20Ranveer%20Singh%20was%20initially%20supposed%20to%20star%20in%20his%20film%20'Bombay%20Velvet'%20but%20was%20replaced%20by%20Ranbir%20Kapoor.%20Kashyap%20mentioned%20that%20Ranveer%20was%20enthusiastic%20about%20the%20project%20and%20had%20even%20memorized%20the%20dialogues.%20However%2C%20due%20to%20budget%20issues%2C%20the%20film%20became%20unsustainable%20and%20Ranbir%20was%20cast%20instead.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fanurag-kashyap-says-ranveer-singh-really-wanted-to-do-bombay-velvet-reveals-why-ranbir-kapoor-replaced-him%2Farticleshow%2F103683489.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Police%20Say%20Peace%20Has%20Been%20Restored%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Satara%2C%20But%20Muslim%20Community%20Still%20in%20Fear%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15120846%2FScreenshot-2023-09-15-at-12.08.15-PM.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20After%20five%20days%20of%20beefed-up%20police%20security%20and%20over%2072-%20hours%20of%20internet%20shutdown%20across%20Satara%20district%20in%20western%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20district%20administration%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpeace%20has%20finally%20been%20restored%E2%80%9D.%20But%20Muslim%20residents%20of%20Pusesavali%20village%2C%20where%20violence%20broke%20out%20on%20September%209%20killing%20one%20youth%20and%20leaving%20several%20injured%2C%20fear%20that%20the%20uneasy%20calm%20can%20turn%20violent%20at%20any%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20September%209%2C%20a%20mob%20of%20Hindu%20men%20ran%20amok%20in%20Pusesavali%20village%20in%20Satara%20district%20after%20an%20objectionable%20post%20against%20King%20Shivaji%20allegedly%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%20Tensions%20based%20on%20the%20post%2C%20allegedly%20put%20out%20by%20a%20Muslim%20youth%2C%20soon%20became%20a%20full-blown%20riot.%20The%20mob%2C%20comprising%20Hindu%20men%20from%20Pursesavali%20and%20neighbouring%20villages%20of%20Thorvewadi%20NV%20and%20Wadgaon%20Jairam%20Swami%2C%20converged%20around%208%20pm%20in%20the%20village%20and%20began%20ransacking%20houses%20and%20commercial%20units%20belonging%20to%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThirty-two-year-old%20Nurul%20Hasan%20Shikalgar%2C%20an%20engineer%20and%20a%20man%20who%20ran%20a%20local%20earthmover%2C%20was%20among%20the%20Muslim%20men%20at%20the%20mosque%20gathered%20to%20offer%20the%20Isha%20(day%E2%80%99s%20last)%20Namaz.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20mob%20had%20sticks%20and%20stones%20in%20their%20hands.%20The%20mosque%20doors%20were%20shut%20but%20they%20applied%20forced%20and%20entered%20the%20space.%20They%20hit%20us%20with%20sharp%20objects%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%2026-year-old%20man%20who%20suffered%20serious%20injuries%20to%20his%20head%20and%20has%20been%20undergoing%20treatment%20at%20a%20local%20hospital.%20Shikalgar%20too%20was%20hit%20on%20his%20head%20many%20times.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20before%20we%20could%20offer%20him%20help%2C%20Nurul%20had%20died%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20339px)%2085vw%2C%20339px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15120936%2FF57GLhwaQAEkS_X.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22339%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15120936%2FF57GLhwaQAEkS_X.jpeg%20720w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15120936%2FF57GLhwaQAEkS_X-249x300.jpeg%20249w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-673153%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22409%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENurul%20Hasan%20Shikalgar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EShikalgar%E2%80%99s%20uncle%20Shiraj%20confirmed%20that%20by%20the%20time%20they%20found%20the%20young%20man%2C%20it%20was%20lying%20%E2%80%9Clifeless%E2%80%9D%20without%20a%20pulse%20or%20heartbeat.%20Shikalgar%20was%20declared%20dead%20at%20the%20local%20Krishna%20Charitable%20Trust%20Hospital%20in%20Satara.%20Disturbed%20by%20Shikalgar%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%20his%20family%20and%20other%20community%20members%20gathered%20at%20the%20hospital%20and%20refused%20to%20move%20the%20body%20for%20cremation%20till%20the%20time%20police%20arrested%20the%20attackers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20rumours%20were%20spread%2C%20especially%20on%20WhatsApp%2C%20that%20Shikalgar%20had%20a%20role%20in%20posting%20objectionable%20posts%20on%20Shivaji.%20But%20a%20senior%20policeman%2C%20privy%20to%20the%20investigation%2C%20confirmed%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Shikalgar%20had%20absolutely%20no%20role%20in%20this.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20looked%20into%20things%20and%20can%20confirm%20he%20just%20became%20a%20victim%20of%20mob%20violence%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20senior%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShikalgar%20was%20one%20of%20the%20few%20educated%20Muslim%20men%20from%20Pusesavali%20village.%20In%20a%20village%20of%20over%201%2C300%20families%2C%20less%20than%2010%25%20belong%20to%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20Most%20of%20them%20run%20the%20local%20village%20businesses%2C%20like%20retail%20stores%20and%20automobile%20spare%20parts%20shops.%20Shikalgar%E2%80%99s%20father%20Liyaqat%20teaches%20at%20a%20local%20Urdu%20school.%20His%20mother%20worked%20as%20a%20nurse%20at%20a%20local%20government%20hospital%20and%20only%20recently%20retired.%C2%A0%20Shikagar%20was%20married%20for%20less%20than%20a%20year%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Ayesha%2C%20is%20five%20months%20pregnant.%20The%20couple%20were%20expecting%20their%20first%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20happened%20in%20Pusesavali%20village%20was%20not%20a%20sudden%20incident.%20Tension%20was%20building%20up%20for%20over%20a%20month%2C%20villagers%20say.%20The%20police%20too%20confirm%20that%20they%20had%20%E2%80%9Canticipated%20the%20worst%E2%80%9D.%20The%20first%20inflammatory%20post%2C%20allegedly%20against%20a%20Hindu%20goddess%2C%20first%20emerged%20on%20social%20media%20on%20August%2015.%20This%20post%2C%20allegedly%20put%20up%20by%20a%20young%20man%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20was%20soon%20taken%20down%20and%20the%20police%20had%20arrested%20the%20person.%20He%20was%20let%20off%20on%20bail%20eventually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%20incident%2C%20a%20representative%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community%20had%20approached%20the%20police.%20In%20the%20representation%2C%20Muslims%20claimed%20that%20they%20%E2%80%9Cfeared%20for%20their%20life%E2%80%9D.%20A%20senior%20policeman%2C%20privy%20to%20the%20investigation%2C%20confirmed%20having%20received%20a%20letter.%20An%20officer%20said%2C%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20%E2%80%9CBut%20in%20the%20letter%20the%20men%20claimed%20that%20they%20had%20threat%20to%20their%20lives%20from%20the%20Hindus.%20It%20was%20a%20generic%20statement.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20that%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Muslim%20community%E2%80%99s%20fears%20came%20true%20on%20September%209.%20Locals%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20say%20that%20the%20way%20in%20which%20the%20mob%20had%20gathered%2C%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20appear%20to%20be%20a%20sudden%20provocation.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20preparedness%20with%20which%20they%20came%20looked%20as%20if%20it%20were%20a%20pre-planned%20attack%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20local%20youth%20from%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20whose%20shop%20was%20one%20of%20those%20destroyed%20in%20the%20attack%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20police%20officer%20said%20that%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20post%20was%20seen%20on%20social%20media%2C%20the%20person%20allegedly%20responsible%20was%20summoned%20to%20the%20police%20station.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20in%20the%20process%20of%20ascertaining%20his%20involvement%20and%20were%20questioning%20him.%20The%20attackers%20meanwhile%20barged%20into%20the%20village%20and%20began%20attacking%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20different%20versions%20on%20the%20origins%20of%20the%20social%20media%20post.%20While%20the%20police%20claim%20they%20acted%20on%20it%20within%20hours%2C%20reporters%20covering%20the%20incident%20say%20the%20post%20first%20emerged%20two%20days%20prior%20to%20the%20incident%20and%20that%20the%20police%20failed%20to%20take%20immediate%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20now%20registered%20three%20different%20FIRs%20after%20the%20September%209%20incident.%20One%20is%20against%20Muslim%20men%20allegedly%20involved%20in%20posting%20objectionable%20content%20against%20King%20Shivaji.%20Another%20FIR%20in%20against%20men%20involved%20in%20Shikalgar%E2%80%99s%20murder%20and%20the%20attack%20at%20the%20mosqu%2Ce%20and%20the%20third%20case%20is%20against%20men%20involved%20in%20attacking%20the%20policemen.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20apprehended%20over%2035%20persons%20in%20all%20three%20cases%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20police%20officer%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15121106%2FSatara-.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15121106%2FSatara-.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15121106%2FSatara--300x144.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F15121106%2FSatara--1024x492.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-673154%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22576%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAftermath%20of%20the%20violence%20on%20Satara.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20internet%20was%20restored%20on%20September%2014%2C%20the%20police%20say%20they%20closely%20monitored%20social%20media%20activities.%20%E2%80%9CNo%20untoward%20activity%20was%20seen%20through%20the%20day%3B%20the%20district%20remained%20calm%20and%20people%20were%20waiting%20to%20resume%20their%20daily%20activities%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20senior%20policeman%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20internet%20shutdown%2C%20the%20local%20administration%20also%20applied%20Section%20144%20of%20the%20CrPC%20prohibiting%20public%20gatherings.%20This%2C%20however%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20deter%20Hindutva%20leaders%20