%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjaahnavi-kandula-indian-student-killed-by-speeding-us-police-car-to-get-degree-posthumously-4391430%5C%22%3E23-year-old%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20hit%20and%20killed%20by%20a%20police%20car%20while%20crossing%20the%20street%20on%20January%2023.%20According%20to%20The%20Seattle%20Times%2C%20Kevin%20Dave%2C%20the%20police%20officer%20driving%20the%20car%20was%20going%20119%20kmph%20and%20the%20graduate%20student's%20body%20was%20thrown%20more%20than%20100%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20is%20the%20statement%20from%20Northeastern%20University%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAs%20many%20of%20you%20know%2C%20last%20January%20our%20student%20Jaahnavi%20Kandula%20was%20killed%20when%20she%20was%20struck%20by%20a%20police%20cruiser%20near%20Northeastern's%20Seattle%20campus.%20In%20the%20days%20following%20this%20tragedy%2C%20our%20Seattle%20campus%20community%20joined%20together%20in%20a%20vigil%20of%20remembrance%20and%20solidarity.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20our%20dean%20Dave%20Thurman%20wrote%20of%20Jaahnavi's%20tremendous%20engagement%2C%20noting%20that%20all%20on%20our%20Seattle%20campus%2C%20%26quot%3Bloved%20her%20bubbly%20laugh%2C%20sense%20of%20humor%20and%20infectious%20personality.%20Her%20loss%20will%20be%20felt%20deeply%20by%20students%2C%20staff%2C%20and%20faculty.%26quot%3B%20The%20university%20plans%20to%20award%20Jaahnavi%20her%20degree%20posthumously%20and%20present%20it%20to%20her%20family.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20week%2C%20Jaahnavi's%20friends%20and%20loved%20ones%20are%20enduring%20the%20additional%20pain%20of%20new%20developments%20related%20to%20this%20tragedy.%20Callous%20and%20insensitive%20remarks%20by%20a%20Seattle%20police%20officer%20have%20become%20public%2C%20reopening%20wounds%20and%20deepening%20our%20collective%20heartbreak.%20We%20also%20recognize%20that%20our%20Indian%20student%20community-across%20all%20Northeastern%20campuses-has%20been%20especially%20impacted%20by%20this%20tragedy%20and%20its%20aftermath.%20We%20stand%20in%20solidarity%20with%20you%20and%20have%20every%20expectation%20that%20the%20ongoing%20investigations%20will%20bring%20a%20measure%20of%20justice%20and%20accountability.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENortheastern%20is%2C%20first%20and%20foremost%2C%20a%20community.%20Our%20pursuit%20of%20knowledge%20is%20infinitely%20enriched%20by%20one%20another-by%20the%20thousands%20of%20learners%20and%20educators%20who%20make%20up%20our%20global%20family.%20When%20a%20group%20of%20us%20are%20experiencing%20anguish%2C%20we%20are%20all%20in%20pain.%20These%20are%20the%20times%20that%20we%20must%20draw%20strength%20from%20each%20other%20and%20move%20forward%20in%20unity.%20Next%20week%2C%20we%20will%20convene%20campus%20gatherings%20to%20allow%20our%20community%20to%20join%20together%20in%20harmony.%20Details%20will%20be%20provided%20soon%20by%20Northeastern%20Student%20Life%20and%20respective%20campus%20deans.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENortheastern%20provides%20a%2024%2F7%20mental%20health%20support%20service%20called%20Find%40Northeastern%20that%20offers%20students%20access%20to%20a%20licensed%20mental%20health%20clinician%20at%20any%20time%20from%20any%20location%20in%20the%20world%20by%20calling%20877.233.9477%E2%80%AF(U.S.)%2C%20855.229.8797(Canada)%2C%E2%80%AF%2B1.781.457.7777%E2%80%AF(Intl.).%20Student%20support%20is%20also%20available%20from%20the%20We%20Care%20team%20in%20Student%20Life%20at%20wecare%40northeastern.edu%20or%20617.373.7591%20as%20well%20through%20the%20Student%20Affairs%20team%20on%20the%20Seattle%20campus%20at%20sea.sa%40northeastern.edu.%20Faculty%20and%20Staff%20can%20contact%20the%20employee%20assistance%20program%20at%20New%20Directions%20at%20800.624.5544.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPlease%20join%20me%20in%20extending%20our%20heartfelt%20condolences%20to%20Jaahnavi's%20family%20and%20friends.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeattle%20Police%20Department%20recently%20released%20bodycam%20footage%20of%20another%20officer%20who%20visited%20the%20accident%20site%20on%20January%2023.%20The%20footage%20has%20created%20a%20furore%20as%20the%20officer%2C%20Daniel%20Auderer%2C%20can%20be%20heard%20laughing%20and%20joking%20about%20the%20incident.%20He%20is%20also%20heard%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20just%20write%20a%20check.%20USD%2011%2C000.%20She%20was%2026%20anyway%2C%20she%20had%20limited%20value.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694758980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F9l726dfg_jaahnavi-kandula_625x300_14_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fjaahnavi-kandula-northeastern-university-remembers-indian-accidentally-killed-by-us-cop-bubbly-laugh-4391837%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Northeastern%20University%20issued%20a%20statement%20remembering%20their%20Indian-origin%20student%20Jaahnavi%20Kandula%2C%20who%20was%20killed%20in%20January%20but%20a%20shocking%20bodycam%20footage%20of%20an%20US%20cop%20laughing%20while%20talking%20about%20her%20death%20was%20recently%20released.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fjaahnavi-kandula-northeastern-university-remembers-indian-accidentally-killed-by-us-cop-bubbly-laugh-4391837%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Over%2050%2C000%20Odisha%20Schools%20Hit%20As%20Government%20Teachers%20Go%20On%20Protest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20indefinite%20strike%20by%20the%20teachers%20has%20affected%20the%20day-to-day%20operations%20in%20over%2050%2C000%20government%20schools%20in%20Odisha.%20The%20teachers%20have%20been%20protesting%20the%20abolition%20of%20the%20contractual%20appointment%20system%20and%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20old%20pension%20scheme%20for%20more%20than%20a%20week.%20The%20strike%20involves%201.30%20lakh%20teachers.%20Despite%20the%20government's%20appeal%2C%20the%20teachers%20have%20refused%20to%20end%20their%20protest.%20They%20started%20the%20strike%20on%20September%208.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20the%20protesting%20teachers%20are%20demanding%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20protesting%20teachers%20are%20demanding%20the%20abolition%20of%20the%20contractual%20appointment%20system.%3Cbr%3EThey%20are%20also%20demanding%20a%20raise%20in%20grade%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20they%20are%20calling%20for%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20old%20pension%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20teachers%20on%20strike%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%2C%20%26quot%3BSince%20the%20government%20failed%20to%20address%20the%20demands%20of%20aggrieved%20teachers%2C%20they%20went%20on%20mass%20leave%20and%20staged%20protests%20before%20the%20offices%20of%20block%20education%20officers%20(BEOs).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20the%20Odisha%20government%20has%20done%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fodishatv.in%2Fnews%2Fodisha%2Fprimary-teachers-across-odisha-intensify-agitation-to-go-on-mass-leave-from-today-214813%5C%22%3EOdisha%20TV%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20state%20government%20has%20set%20up%20a%20sub-committee%20of%20five%20members%20to%20review%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20protesting%20teachers.%20The%20committee%20will%20submit%20its%20report%20to%20the%20inter-ministerial%20panel%2C%20and%20then%20the%20government%20will%20make%20the%20final%20decision%20regarding%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20teachers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20protesting%20teacher%20said%20that%20instead%20of%20addressing%20their%20demands%2C%20the%20government%20had%20constituted%20a%20sub-committee.%20He%20questioned%20the%20necessity%20of%20the%20sub-committee%20when%20an%20inter-ministerial%20panel%20had%20already%20been%20formed.%20He%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20sub-committee%20was%20created%20%26quot%3Bonly%20to%20delay%20the%20process%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpposition%20parties%20slam%20Odisha%20government%20over%20teachers'%20strike%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20have%20both%20criticised%20the%20Odisha%20government%20over%20the%20issue.%20BJP%20spokesperson%20Anil%20Biswal%20said%20the%20state%20government%20had%20failed%20to%20address%20the%20grievances%20of%20protesting%20teachers.%20He%20slammed%20the%20state%20government%20for%20spending%20Rs%20500%20crore%20on%20the%20chopper%20ride%20of%20a%20secretary%20while%20being%20unable%20to%20provide%20proper%20salaries%20to%20teachers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EState%20Congress%20president%20Sarat%20Pattanayaks%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BEducation%20system%20in%20Odisha%20is%20facing%20an%20'emergency'%20like%20situation%2C%20and%20the%20government%20is%20not%20taking%20appropriate%20measures%20to%20resolve%20their%20issues.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ERuling%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%20MLA%20Arabinda%20Dhali%20asserted%20that%20the%20state%20government%20would%20certainly%20look%20into%20the%20genuine%20demands%20of%20the%20protesting%20teachers.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlock%20Education%20Officers%20directed%20to%20submit%20daily%20report%20of%20each%20teacher%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20Block%20Education%20Officers%20(BEOs)%20have%20been%20directed%20by%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Elementary%20Education%20of%20the%20Odisha%20government%20to%20submit%20a%20daily%20report%20of%20each%20teacher%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkalingatv.com%2Fstate%2Fteachers-strike-in-odisha-beos-asked-to-submit-daily-report-of-each-teacher%2F%5C%22%3EKalinga%20TV%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20Director%20of%20Elementary%20Education%2C%20Brundaban%20Satapathy%2C%20instructed%20the%20BEOs%20to%20keep%20records%20of%20teachers%20who%20are%20absent%20from%20school%20due%20to%20the%20strike%20and%20those%20who%20have%20attended%20and%20performed%20their%20duties%2C%20particularly%20the%20contractual%20teachers.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694758920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Ff2cp95g8_school-representative-image_625x300_11_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fover-50-000-odisha-schools-hit-as-government-teachers-go-on-protest-4391801%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Teachers'%20strike%20in%20Odisha%3A%20All%20Block%20Education%20Officers%20(BEOs)%20have%20been%20directed%20to%20submit%20a%20daily%20report%20of%20each%20teacher.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fover-50-000-odisha-schools-hit-as-government-teachers-go-on-protest-4391801%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fover-50-000-odisha-schools-hit-as-government-teachers-go-on-protest-4391801%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fover-50-000-odisha-schools-hit-as-government-teachers-go-on-protest-4391801%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Netflix%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20Yash%20Raj%20Films%20Launch%20Multi-Year%20Creative%20Partnership%20With%20%E2%80%98The%20Railway%20Men%2C%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98Maharaj%E2%80%99%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694758800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2FThe-Railway-Men.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235723624%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Netflix%20and%20leading%20Indian%20studio%20Yash%20Raj%20Films%20(YRF)%20have%20set%20a%20multi-year%20creative%20partnership.%20The%20two%20entities%20will%20%E2%80%9Ccollaborate%20to%20create%20films%20and%20series%20to%20bring%20defining%20stories%20to%20audiences%20in%20India%20and%20across%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20The%20partnership%20will%20kick%20off%20with%20four-part%20thriller%