most%20respected%20former%20chairmen%20has%20said%20reportage%20by%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F8d46b435-9725-46d4-80be-2cb3e276c4c9%5C%22%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0based%20on%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.occrp.org%2Fen%2Finvestigations%2Fdocuments-provide-fresh-insight-into-allegations-of-stock-manipulation-that-rocked-indias-powerful-adani-group%5C%22%3Edocuments%20shared%20by%20the%20Organised%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Report%20Project%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20raises%20disturbing%20questions%20and%20makes%20worrying%20allegations%20about%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20is%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20persuasive%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0report%2C%20M.%20Damodaran%20said%20it%20is%20%E2%80%9Cwell-compiled%20and%20a%20credit%20to%20those%20who%20put%20it%20together%E2%80%9D.%20He%20said%20there%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Ca%20presumption%20some%20of%20this%20is%20correct%E2%80%9D.%20However%2C%20Damodaran%20added%20that%20as%20yet%20the%20report%20is%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20conclusive%E2%80%9D%2C%20explaining%20that%20the%20distance%20between%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20persuasive%E2%80%9D%20and%20not%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20conclusive%E2%80%9D%20must%20be%20covered%20by%20a%20thorough%20and%20diligent%20investigation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20a%2030-minute%20interview%20to%20Karan%20Thapar%20for%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Wire%3Cem%3E%2C%20Damodaran%2C%20who%20is%20at%20present%20the%20director%20of%20companies%20such%20as%20Larsen%20and%20Toubro%2C%20Hero%20MotoCorp%2C%20Tech%20Mahindra%2C%20CRISIL%20and%20Biocon%20and%20non-executive%20chairman%20of%20IndiGo%2C%20said%20this%20is%20%E2%80%9Cclearly%20a%20matter%20for%20investigation%20and%20it%20must%20be%20done%20quickly%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EHe%20added%20%E2%80%9Cmost%20if%20not%20all%20elements%20(of%C2%A0the%20%3C%2Fem%3EFinancial%20Times%3Cem%3E%C2%A0story)%20need%20to%20be%20looked%20at.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20is%20a%20transcript%20of%20the%20interview.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20style%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKaran%20Thapar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Hello%20and%20welcome%20to%20a%20special%20interview%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%20On%20the%2031st%20of%20August%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%93%20arguably%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20best%20known%20and%20most%20highly%20regarded%20financial%20paper%20%E2%80%93%20published%20a%20story%20raising%20worrying%20questions%20and%20disturbing%20allegations%20about%20the%20Adani%20Group.%20That%20story%20simply%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20got%20the%20attention%20it%20deserves%20in%20our%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20types%20of%20issues%20were%20raised%3A%20first%2C%20are%20the%20total%20shareholdings%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20the%20promoters%20of%20the%20group%2C%20above%20SEBI%20%5BSecurities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%5D%20stipulations%3F%20Secondly%2C%20if%20that%20is%20the%20case%2C%20does%20it%20suggest%20share%20price%20manipulation%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoining%20me%20to%20discuss%20the%20allegations%20and%20the%20credibility%20with%20which%20they%E2%80%99ve%20been%20made%2C%20and%20what%20SEBI%20and%20the%20government%20should%20do%20in%20response%2C%20is%20the%20former%20chairman%20of%20SEBI%2C%20M.%20Damodaran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMr%20Damodaran%2C%20as%20I%20said%20in%20that%20introduction%2C%20an%20article%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%2031st%20of%20August%20based%20on%20documents%20shared%20by%20the%20Organised%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%20(OCCRP)%20has%20once%20again%20raised%20disturbing%20questions%20and%20allegations%20about%20the%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20article%20reveals%20that%20two%20men%20%E2%80%93%20Nasir%20Ali%20Shaban%20Ahli%20of%20the%20UAE%20and%20Chang%20Chung%20Ling%20of%20Taiwan%20%E2%80%93%20have%20spent%20years%20trading%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%E2%80%99%20worth%20of%20Adani%20stock.%20The%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20describes%20them%20as%20associates%20of%20Vinod%20Adani%20and%20says%20their%20investments%20were%20overseen%20by%20a%20Vinod%20Adani%20employee.%20The%20paper%20says%20this%20raises%20questions%20about%20whether%20they%20are%20frontmen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20you%E2%80%99ve%20read%20these%20reports%2C%20so%20can%20I%20start%20by%20asking%20how%20credible%20are%20the%20reasons%20for%20suspecting%20that%20these%20are%20frontmen%20for%20the%20Adani%20family%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EM.%20Damodaran%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20First%20of%20all%2C%20the%20report%20is%20very%20well-compiled.%20I%20think%20one%20must%20give%20credit%20to%20those%20that%20put%20it%20together.%20Secondly%2C%20it%20is%20a%20very%20persuasive%20report.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20one%20that%20you%20can%20read%20and%20put%20aside%20because%20I%20think%20it%20raises%20interesting%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FF-_2-7Wgb_0%3Fsi%3DkqVN2nZpkBsMYHx0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20between%20being%20persuasive%20and%20being%20conclusive%2C%20there%20is%20an%20area%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20addressed.%20I%20think%20this%20is%20what%20we%20need%20to%20look%20at.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAre%20these%20persons%20frontmen%3F%20Well%2C%20I%20think%20what%20happens%20in%20circumstantial%20evidence%20is%20you%20have%20to%20put%20everything%20together.%20No%20link%20must%20be%20weak.%20So%20every%20relationship%20that%20exists%20in%20this%20chain%20of%20relationships%20needs%20to%20be%20examined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20possible%20that%20they%20are%20frontmen%2C%20possible%20that%20there%20were%20transactions%20in%20shares%20made%20by%20funds%20that%20went%20out%20of%20India%2C%20which%20then%20makes%20it%20a%20case%20of%20round%20tripping.%20Clearly%20there%20are%20issues%20of%20whether%20the%2075%25%20limit%20that%20the%20promoters%20and%20promoter%20group%20can%20hold%20%E2%80%93%20has%20that%20been%20violated%20by%20resorting%20to%20this%20stratagem%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20all%20issues%20that%20have%20been%20flagged%20in%20the%20report.%20Related%20party%20transactions%20(RPT)%2C%20I%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20for%20these%20to%20be%20looked%20at.%20The%20report%20itself%2C%20I%20will%20not%20say%20is%20conclusive.%20It%20raises%20a%20number%20of%20issues.%20At%20best%2C%20there%20can%20be%20a%20presumption%20that%20some%20of%20this%20is%20correct.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20is%20there%20a%20proof%20beyond%20doubt%20or%20is%20this%20preponderance%20of%20probability%20%E2%80%93%20what%20is%20the%20degree%20of%20proof%20that%20you%20need%3F%20These%20are%20the%20number%20of%20related%20questions%20you%20need%20to%20%5Binaudible%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Would%20I%20be%20right%20in%20saying%20that%20you%20therefore%20believe%20that%20the%20issues%20raised%20need%20to%20be%20examined%20thoroughly%3F%20That%20the%20suspicions%20justify%20a%20thorough%20investigation%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20would%20say%20what%20the%20report%20has%20brought%20out%20certainly%20needs%20to%20be%20investigated.%20It%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20brushed%20aside%2C%20not%20just%20because%20it%20concerns%20one%20big%20group%20in%20India%2C%20but%20to%20see%20whether%20there%20are%20systemic%20issues%20that%20need%20to%20be%20plugged%20to%20ensure%20minimum%20public%20shareholding%20(MPS)%20of%2025%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20this%20can%20be%20used%20as%20a%20case%20in%20which%20you%20can%20examine%20what%20are%20the%20ways%20in%20which%20people%20are%20getting%20around%20or%20can%20get%20around%20minimum%20public%20shareholding%20of%2025%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECertainly%2C%20several%20aspects%20that%20need%20to%20be%20looked%20into%20%E2%80%93%20there%20are%20allegations%20of%20related%20party%20transactions.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20%5Binaudible%5D%20of%20disclosure.%20If%20some%20of%20this%20had%20happened%2C%20has%20it%20been%20disclosed%2C%20have%20the%20auditors%20looked%20at%20it%2C%20has%20the%20board%20looked%20at%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20imagine%20that%20the%20board%20comprising%20several%20eminent%20persons%20would%2C%20after%20the%20report%20came%20out%20at%20least%2C%20have%20addressed%20some%20of%20these%20issues%20or%20looked%20into%20it%20or%20set%20in%20motion%20a%20kind%20of%20enquiry%20to%20determine%20whether%20this%20is%20right%20and%20actionable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadanis-acquisitions-the-inorganic-strategy-behind-the-purchase-of-gangavaram-port%5C%22%3EAdani%E2%80%99s%20Acquisitions%3A%20The%20%E2%80%98Inorganic%20Strategy%E2%80%99%20Behind%20the%20Purchase%20of%20Gangavaram%20Port%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Let%20me%2C%20Mr.%20Damodaran%2C%20put%20one%20or%20two%20of%20the%20points%20made%20in%20that%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20story%20to%20you.%20The%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20says%2C%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20quoting%2C%20%E2%80%9CAccording%20to%20%5Bthe%5D%20documents%2C%20in%20January%202017%20Ahli%20and%20Chung%2C%20secretly%20controlled%20at%20least%2013%25%20of%20the%20free%20float%20%E2%80%A6%20in%20three%20out%20of%20%5Bthe%5D%20four%20Adani%20companies%20listed%20on%20the%20stock%20exchange%20at%20that%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoesn%E2%80%99t%20this%20mean%20that%20if%20these%20men%20were%20fronts%20for%20the%20Adani%20family%2C%20its%20shareholding%20will%20have%20substantially%20breached%20the%20SEBI%20regulation%20%E2%80%93%20that%2025%25%20of%20shares%20must%20be%20freely%20traded%20and%20in%20public%20hands%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20this%20is%20established%20%E2%80%93%20at%20present%20and%20as%20you%20said%20in%20your%20introductory%20remarks%2C%20these%20are%20allegations%20%E2%80%93%20if%20this%20is%20established%2C%20then%20clearly%20there%20is%20some%20cause%20of%20action%20that%20arises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20difficult%20to%20prove%20this%20or%20this%20cannot%20be%20proved%2C%20then%20I%20think%20we%20should%20not%20draw%20too%20many%20conclusions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20important%20in%20my%20view%20is%20to%20note%20that%20SEBI%20has%20looked%20at%20all%20the%20points%20that%20they%20were%20expected%20to%20look%20at%20except%20two%2C%20and%20they%20are%20to%20file%20a%20report%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20already%20filed%20one%20which%20says%20we%20need%20a%20little%20more%20time%20to%20look%20at%20two%20of%20these%20because%20we%E2%80%99ve%20sought%20information%20from%20overseas%20regulators%2C%20they%20haven%E2%80%99t%20come%20in%20yet%2C%20and%20therefore%20we%20cannot%20put%20it%20all%20together%20and%20draw%20conclusions%20in%20your%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20would%20want%20to%20wait%20till%20SEBI%20puts%20this%20together%2C%20see%20what%20they%E2%80%99ve%20got%20and%20what%20conclusions%20they%20draw%2C%20because%20they%E2%80%99re%20going%20to%20file%20it%20with%20the%20highest%20court%20of%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Absolutely.%20Now%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20take%20the%20example%20of%20Adani%20Enterprises%2C%20which%20is%20the%20flagship%20company.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%20January%202017%20the%20promoters%20owned%2074.9%25%2C%20which%20meant%20that%20the%20free%20float%20should%20have%20been%2025.1%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20says%20that%20it%20turns%20out%20that%20of%20that%2025.1%25%20free%20float%2C%2013.5%25