20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20whether%20closure%20was%20applied%2C%20but%20certainly%2C%20it%20looked%20like%20there%20was%20a%20plausible%20explanation%20given%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%5Binaudible%5D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20is%20one%20element.%20RPT%20certainly%20needs%20to%20be%20looked%20at.%20If%20there%20are%20allegations%20that%20these%20are%20related%20parties%20and%20they%20have%20done%20transactions%2C%20you%20need%20to%20look%20at%20them%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20important.%20What%20is%20within%20SEBIs%20remit%20is%20clearly%20RPT%2C%20is%20clearly%20MPS%2C%20is%20clearly%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20transactions%20have%20been%20conducted%2C%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20sure%20it%20is%20a%20work-in-progress%20%5Binaudible%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdoes-the-mention-of-an-adani-connection-trigger-the-modi-government%5C%22%3EDoes%20the%20Mention%20of%20an%20Adani%20Connection%20Trigger%20the%20Modi%20Government%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Can%20I%20reach%20the%20second%20issue%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20raises%3F%20If%20these%20are%20frontmen%20and%20if%2C%20therefore%2C%20it%20transpires%20the%20shareholding%20of%20the%20Adani%20family%2C%20the%20promoters%2C%20has%20exceeded%20SEBI%20stipulations%2C%20does%20that%20also%20then%20hint%20towards%20share%20price%20manipulation%3F%20Is%20that%20a%20legitimised%20suspicion%20to%20have%20in%20mind%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECertainly%2C%20people%20that%20both%20OCCRP%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20have%20spoken%20to%20%E2%80%93%20these%20are%20Indian%20authorities%20%E2%80%93%20believe%20that%20if%20the%20shareholding%20of%20the%20family%20has%20crossed%2075%25%2C%20then%20there%20%5Bare%5D%20clearly%20grounds%20to%20suspect%20share%20price%20manipulation.%20Would%20you%20agree%20that%20that%E2%80%99s%20a%20legitimate%20second%20suspicion%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Let%20me%20move%20away%20from%20this%20particular%20case%20and%20look%20at%20why%20MPS%20exists.%20Twenty-five%20percent%20public%20shareholding%20of%20an%20entity%20that%20is%20listed%20in%20the%20securities%20market%20is%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20a%20method%20by%20which%20you%20can%20help%20to%20establish%20what%20should%20be%20the%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20if%20that%20is%20breached%2C%20if%20persons%20are%20investing%20in%20the%20stocks%2C%20if%20the%20promoter%20and%20the%20promoter%20group%20together%20hold%20more%20than%2075%25%2C%20clearly%20they%20are%20in%20a%20position%20to%20influence%20the%20prices.%20Because%20it%20is%20a%20very%20large%20chunk%2C%20above%2075%25%2C%20if%20you%20get%20to%2080-83%25%20to%20the%20numbers%20that%20you%20mentioned%2C%20would%20take%20it%20closer%20to%2085%25%20or%20even%20above%20that%20I%20imagine.%20Clearly%20you%20are%20in%20a%20position%20to%20influence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIs%20this%20the%20only%20group%20that%20has%20this%20situation%3F%20No.%20Several%20others%20also%20have%2C%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20come%20in%20to%20the%20public.%20Government%20undertakings%2C%20of%20course%2C%20are%20exempt%20and%20therefore%20government%20continues%20as%20a%20majority%20shareholder%20and%20%5Bholds%5D%20above%2090%25%20in%20several%20entities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWill%20this%20lead%20automatically%3F%20%5Bsic%5D%20It%20can%20be%20an%20instrument.%20Has%20it%20happened%3F%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20So%20what%20you%E2%80%99re%20saying%2C%20Mr%20Damodaran%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20just%20simplifying%20it%20for%20the%20audience%20who%20may%20not%20be%20technically%20proficient%2C%20if%20the%20shareholding%20of%20the%20Adani%20group%2C%20the%20promoters%2C%20is%20in%20excess%20of%2075%25%2C%20then%20clearly%20there%20are%20grounds%20to%20suspect%20%E2%80%93%20only%20suspect%20%E2%80%93%20that%20there%20could%20be%20share%20price%20manipulation%2C%20and%20that%20is%20therefore%20something%20else%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20looked%20into.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Oh%2C%20clearly%20that%20is%20an%20aspect%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20looked%20into%2C%20because%20if%20you%20have%20a%20very%2C%20very%20large%20shareholding%20in%20the%20promoted%20group%2C%20clearly%20that%20can%20impact%20on%20share%20prices.%20Now%2C%20is%20that%20manipulation%2C%20are%20there%20things%20that%20are%20done%20in%20order%20to%20push%20prices%20up%2C%20and%20therefore%20you%20get%20other%20people%20to%20buy%20in%2C%20it%20gives%20the%20group%20much%20better%20numbers%20in%20the%20market.%20These%20are%20issues%20that%20need%20to%20be%20investigated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20as%20you%20said%20rightly%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20suspicion%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20an%20allegation%2C%20but%20the%20report%E2%80%99s%20been%20put%20together%20well.%20I%20must%20say%20a%20lot%20of%20documents%20have%20been%20looked%20at%20and%20that%20is%20why%20I%20said%20at%20the%20outset%20%5Bthat%20it%20is%5D%20very%20persuasive.%20Is%20it%20conclusive%3F%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20so%20sure%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20for%20the%20regulator%20to%20find.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14191306%2FSEBI-Bhavan-1024x768.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14191306%2FSEBI-Bhavan-1024x768.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14191306%2FSEBI-Bhavan-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F14191306%2FSEBI-Bhavan.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-673093%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESEBI%20headquarters%20in%20Mumbai.%20Photo%3A%20Jimmy%20Vikas%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20CC%20BY-SA%203.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Absolutely%2C%20but%20the%20distance%2C%20as%20you%20said%2C%20between%20very%20persuasive%20and%20conclusive%2C%20is%20a%20distance%20that%20must%20be%20covered%20by%20investigation%20and%20that%20investigation%20has%20to%20be%20done%20by%20regulators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20That%E2%80%99s%20absolutely%20correct%2C%20because%20if%20there%20is%20so%20much%20information%20that%20is%20coming%20out%20in%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20clearly%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20matter%20for%20investigation.%20I%20would%20go%20one%20step%20further%20and%20say%20that%20these%20investigations%20ought%20to%20be%20conducted%20quickly%2C%20so%20that%20confidence%20in%20the%20market%20is%20not%20adversely%20impacted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20second-guess%20the%20regulator%20on%20this.%20I%20am%20sure%20they%20seize%20of%20the%20matter%20and%20especially%20since%20this%20is%20a%20matter%20where%20they%20are%20to%20report%20back%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20saying%20that%20we%E2%80%99ve%20completed%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20let%20me%20remind%20you%20that%20a%20six-member%20committee%20of%20experts%20headed%20by%20a%20retired%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20had%20looked%20at%20some%20aspects%20of%20this%20%E2%80%93%20arising%20out%20of%20this%2C%20the%20brief%20that%20was%20given%20to%20them%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20and%20then%20concluded%20that%20there%20is%20no%20evidence%20that%20the%20regulator%20had%20been%20ignoring%20what%20it%20needed%20to%20%5Binaudible%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20of%20course%2C%20they%20went%20off%20on%20a%20tangent%20to%20talk%20about%20how%20to%20protect%20investors%2C%20what%20to%20do%20with%20people%20whose%20shares%20had%20been%20lost%2C%20all%20of%20which%20I%20think%20was%20completely%20unnecessary%20because%20it%20took%20the%20eye%20off%20the%20ball.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20needed%20to%20focus%20on%20the%20principal%20requirement%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20asked%20them%20to%20look%20at%2C%20which%20was%20the%20regulator%20measuring%20up%2C%20and%20I%20think%20the%20report%20%E2%80%93%20I%20won%E2%80%99t%20say%20it%20gives%20the%20regulator%20a%20clean%20chit%20%E2%80%93%20but%20certainly%20comes%20to%20a%20conclusion%20that%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20evidence%20to%20show%20the%20regulator%20%5Binaudible%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20But%20now%2C%20actually%2C%20we%20have%20very%20good%20grounds%20given%20to%20us%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20to%20be%20honest%2C%20given%20to%20us%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EGuardian%20%3C%2Fem%3Eas%20well%2C%20and%20all%20of%20this%20put%20together%20for%20both%20papers%20by%20the%20Organised%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20these%20are%20credible%20grounds%20for%20suspicion%20which%20require%20in-depth%2C%20honest%2C%20diligent%20and%20thorough%20investigation.%20If%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20do%20that%2C%20we%20will%20be%20remiss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20would%20think%20we%20should%20not%20jump%20to%20conclusions%20and%20think%20that%20that%20is%20not%20being%20done%20%E2%80%93%20an%20honest%20diligent%2C%20investigation%20as%20you%20put%20it.%20The%20problem%20is%20some%20of%20this%20takes%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Sure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEspecially%20because%20you%E2%80%99ve%20got%20to%20collect%20information%20from%20overseas%20regulators%2C%20and%20SEBI%20has%20said%20as%20much%20in%20its%20report%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20It%20said%20that%20in%20these%20two%20cases%2C%20we%20need%20to%20get%20in%20from%20these%20two%20items%20in%20our%20inquiry%2C%20the%20others%20they%20have%20said%20our%20report%20%5Binaudible%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Can%20I%20put%20to%20you%2C%20sir%2C%20two%20other%20facts%20before%20I%20move%20to%20something%20else%2C%20and%20ask%20you%20whether%20these%20two%20are%20the%20facts%20reported%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20grounds%20for%20believing%20this%20suspicion%20%E2%80%93%20that%20these%20two%20men%20are%20fronts%20%E2%80%93%20could%20be%20correct.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20is%20this%3A%20according%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20these%20two%20men%20Ahli%20and%20Chung%2C%20made%20their%20investments%20in%20Adani%20companies%20through%20two%20funds.%20The%20two%20funds%20are%20the%20Emerging%20India%20Focus%20Fund%20and%20the%20EM%20Resurgent%20Fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EFT%3C%2Fem%3E%20says%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20quoting%2C%20%E2%80%9CBehind%20the%20scenes%2C%20all%20but%20two%20million%20dollars%20out%20of%20260%20million%20dollars%20in%20Adani%20stock%20held%20by%20the%20funds%20in%20September%202014%20were%20controlled%20by%20Ali%20and%20Chung%E2%80%99s%20companies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20question%20is%20this%2C%20is%20this%20huge%20and%20deliberate%20investment%20in%20Adani%20stock%20another%20reason%20for%20suspecting%20Ahli%20and%20Chung%20are%20frontmen%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%20I%20think%20you%20need%20to%20also%20look%20at%E2%80%A6%20This%20is%20an%20issue%20that%20has%20not%20been%20addressed.%20How%20were%20these%20funds%20set%20up%3F%20Did%20these%20funds%20invite%20public%20investment%3F%20If%20so%2C%20what%20is%20it%20that%20was%20promised%3F%20Because%20there%20are%20funds%20that%20have%20significant%20investment%20in%20some%20companies%20and%20small%20investments%20in%20some%20other%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20by%20itself%20is%20not%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20say%2C%20violative%20of%20any%20regulations%20unless%20the%20constitution%20of%20the%20fund%20itself%20says%20that%20you%20should%20be%20widely%20dispersed%2C%20just%20the%20kind%20of%20directions%20you%20have%20for%20mutual%20funds%2C%20for%20example%20%E2%80%93%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20have%20concentration%20beyond%20a%20certain%20level%20in%20a%20particular%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20there%20are%20other%20regulators%20that%20also%20need%20to%20look%20at%20these.%20Overseas%20regulators%20need%20to%20look%20at%20what%20was%20happening%2C%20because%20I%20would%20imagine%20that%20information%20sharing%20under%20the%20memorandum%20of%20understanding%20that%20IOSCO%20%5BInternational%20Organization%20of%20Securities%20Commissions%5D%20has%20should%20enable%20regulators%20to%20share%20information%20that%20is%20critical%20for%20the%20stability%20and%20growth%20of%20the%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20SEBI%20seized%20of%20all%20of%20this.%20I%20think%20they%E2%80%99re%20working%20it%20in%E2%80%A6%20The%20nature%20of%20the%20investigation%20is%20such%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20time-taking%20because%20they%20need%20%E2%80%93%20I%E2%80%99m%20saying%20what%20they%20have%20told%20the%20court%20%E2%80%93%20to%20get%20information%20from%20outside%20regulators%20and%20that%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20come%20in%20%5Binaudible%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Fmodi-adani-oligarchy-stock-offshore%5C%22%3EThe%20Undeniable%20Rise%20of%20Oligarchic%20Capitalism%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Let%20me%20put%20the%20second%20fact%20to%20you%2C%20again%20to%20ask%20whether%20the%20second%20fact%20corroborates%20the%20suspicion%20that%20these%20two%20men%20are%20fronts.%20According%20to%20the%3Cem%3E%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Ahli%20and%20Chung%E2%80%99s%20investments%20were%20overseen%20by%20an%20employee%20of%20Excel%20Investment%20and%20Advisory%20Services%2C%20which%20is%20a%20Vinod%20Adani%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Excel%20was%20paid%20an%20advisory%20fee%20related%20to%20these%20investments.%20In%20fact%2C%20OCCRP%20goes%20one%20step%20further%20%E2%80%93%20it%20says%20the%20agreement%20between%20Excel%20and%20the%20funds%20used%20by%20Ahli%20and%20Chung%20was%20signed%20by%20Vinod%20Adani%20himself.%20Is%20that%20another%20reason%20for%20saying%20this%20suspicion%20that%20the%20two%20men%20are%20fronts%20is%20one%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20seriously%20investigated%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It%20certainly%20needs%20to%20be%20investigated.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20anyone%E2%80%99s%20case%20that%20you%20can%20brush%20it%20aside%2C%20ignore%20it%2C%20turn%20a%20Nelson%E2%80%99s%20eye%E2%80%A6%20no%2C%20certainly%20not.%20But%20does%20that%20lead%20us%20to%20conclude%20that%20these%20were%20frontmen%2C%20that%20these%20were%20Vinod%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20persons%2C%20that%20Vinod%20Adani%20had%20used%20them%20in%20order%20to%20invest%20money%20and%20that%20it%20was%20meant%20for%20violating%20the%20MPS%20etc.%3F%20I%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20matter%20for%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20you%20said%20rightly%2C%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20elements%20in%20this%20report.%20Most%20of%20these%20elements%2C%20if%20not%20all%2C%20need%20to%20be%20looked%20at%20by%20someone%20who%20has%20both%20the%20responsibility%20as%20well%20as%20the%20skill%20sets%20to%20get%20to%20whatever%20is%20the%20truth.%20Until%20that%20emerges%2C%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20jump%20to%20conclusions%20and%20say%20this%20is%20open%20and%20shut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENo%2C%20absolutely%20not.%20These%20are%20just%20suspicions%20that%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYeah.%20Because%20it%E2%80%99s%20entirely%20possible%E2%80%A6%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20well-researched%20report%2C%20let%20me%20say%20that.%20But%20a%20well-researched%20report%20that%20throws%20up%20facts%20and%20information%2C%20it%20does%20not%20present%20a%20complete%20enough%20