n%20the%20right%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ffresh-adani-revelations-that-hint-at-regulator-sebi-inaction-could-hurt-indias-fatf-credibility%5C%22%3EFresh%20Adani%20Revelations%20that%20Hint%20at%20Regulator%20SEBI%20Inaction%20Could%20Hurt%20India%E2%80%99s%20FATF%20Credibility%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20But%20you%E2%80%99re%20saying%2C%20by%20that%20very%20carefully%20crafted%20answer%2C%20that%20the%20SEBI%20will%20do%20it%20diligently%20%5Band%5D%20thoroughly%2C%20but%20you%E2%80%99re%20not%20so%20sure%20they%E2%80%99ll%20do%20it%20quickly%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Well%2C%20I%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20beast.%20You%E2%80%99ve%20got%20to%20get%20information%20from%20various%20places%2C%20and%20unlike%20persons%20like%20me%20who%20are%20now%20outside%20the%20system%20%5Band%5D%20who%20can%20jump%20to%20conclusions%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20SEBI%20can%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20must%2C%20in%20these%20matters%2C%20build%20a%20watertight%20case%20that%20survives%20scrutiny%20at%20the%20appellate%20level%2C%20and%20perhaps%20it%20will%20even%20if%20there%20is%20a%20case%20against%20somebody%2C%20it%20travels%20right%20up%20to%20the%20apex%20court%2C%20where%20it%20will%20have%20to%20be%20defended.%20Therefore%2C%20all%20of%20that%20clearly%20will%20take%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELet%20me%20tell%20you%20why%20some%20people%20have%20doubts%20not%20just%20about%20the%20speed%20with%20which%20SEBI%20will%20investigate%2C%20but%20also%20the%20diligence%20and%20the%20thoroughness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20is%20the%20reason%3A%20the%20%3Cem%3EFT%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%20revealed%20and%20so%20did%20OCCRP%20as%20well%20as%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EGuardian%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20that%20SEBI%2C%20as%20far%20back%20as%20January%202014%2C%20was%20informed%