nt%20would%20have%20looked%20at%20what%20is%20actionable%20at%20the%20level%20of%20the%20government%2C%20what%20is%20actionable%20at%20the%20level%20of%20different%20regulators.%20I%E2%80%99m%20sure%20all%20of%20that%20is%20something%20that%20is%20happening%20within%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20let%20me%20also%20say%20this%2C%20that%20if%20there%20was%20such%20concern%20as%20the%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20says%2C%20that%20investors%20would%20have%20post%20the%20publication%20of%20this%20report%20%E2%80%93%20this%20report%E2%80%99s%20been%20around%20for%20some%20time%2C%20not%20that%20it%20happened%20yesterday%20only%20%E2%80%93%20you%20would%20have%20seen%20some%20impact%20of%20that%20by%20way%20of%20some%20funds%20moving%20out%20of%20India.%20Nothing%20of%20the%20kind%20is%20happening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20there%20have%20been%20significant%20investments%20in%20the%20market.%20There%20have%20been%20significant%20announcements%20regarding%20impending%20FDI.%20So%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20portfolio%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20foreign%20direct%20investment.%20And%20therefore%2C%20the%20confidence%20in%20the%20Indian%20system%20that%20India%20is%20in%20the%20vanguard%20of%20the%20growth%20economies%2C%20none%20of%20that%20will%20go%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20these%20allegations%20will%20have%20to%20be%20investigated.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20my%20case%20that%20this%20has%20to%20be%20ignored%20%E2%80%93%20far%20from%20it.%20And%20I%E2%80%99m%20sure%20that%20somebody%20is%20working%20on%20it%20quietly%2C%20unseen%20by%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Mr%20Damodaran%2C%20thank%20you%20very%20much%20for%20agreeing%20to%20this%20interview.%20Thank%20you%20very%20much%20also%20for%20helping%20us%20understand%20and%20appreciate%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20suspicions%20and%20allegations%20which%20are%20not%20conclusive%2C%20but%20as%20you%20said%2C%20they%20are%20very%20persuasive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20as%20