ward%20for%20Teachers%202023%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EArchana%20was%20able%20to%20convince%20the%20parents%20and%20the%20children%20soon%20started%20coming%20to%20school.%20However%2C%20she%20soon%20started%20seeing%20students%20drop%20out.%20On%20enquiry%2C%20she%20realised%20that%20transportation%20was%20a%20major%20challenge.%20How%20would%20these%20children%20come%20to%20the%20school%20which%20was%20over%205%20km%20away%20with%20just%20a%20%3Cem%3Ekaccha%20%3C%2Fem%3Eroad%20leading%20to%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20solve%20this%20problem%2C%20Archana%20arranged%20an%20auto%20to%20pick%20up%20and%20drop%20off%20the%20students%20daily%2C%20at%20her%20own%20expense.%20Through%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327999%2Famerican-english-teacher-elizabeth-keyton-started-elikutty-to-learn-and-teach-malayalam-instagram%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etireless%20efforts%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20ensure%20that%20the%20tribal%20students%20in%20the%20village%20are%20educated%2C%20she%20has%20increased%20the%20strength%20to%20275%20students%20today%2C%20with%20103%20being%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20this%2C%20she%20also%20worked%20on%20developing%20the%20school%20infrastructure.%20For%20this%2C%20she%20enlisted%20the%20help%20of%20a%20former%20student%20of%20her%20school%2C%20Rajendra%20Prasad%2C%20who%20now%20lives%20abroad.%20NGOs%20like%20Bring%20a%20Smile%20Foundation%2C%20Padmavati%20Charitable%20Trust%20and%20local%20politicians%20also%20joined%20hands%20to%20support%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20able%20to%20procure%20a%20borewell%2C%20purified%20water%20plant%2C%20furniture%2C%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20built%20a%20beautiful%20library%20with%201000%20books%2C%20through%20their%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRajendra%20has%20helped%20tremendously%20in%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20school.%20He%20is%20the%20person%20through%20whom%20we%20got%20most%20of%20the%20donations.%20The%20Washington%20Telangana%20Association%20(WATA)%20helped%20us%20get%2040%20benches%20for%20the%20school%20because%20of%20his%20efforts.%20A%20local%20MLA%20installed%20the%20borewell%20and%20an%20RO%20plant%20in%20the%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20learning%20more%20fun%2C%20through%20digital%20technology%20and%20the%20central%20government%E2%80%99s%20Information%20and%20Communication%20Technology%20(ICT)%20initiative%2C%20she%20procured%20five%20computers%2C%20two%20LED%20projectors%20and%20two%20additional%20classrooms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ICT%20Information%20and%20Communication%20Technology%20School%20Scheme%20was%20launched%20in%20December%202004%20to%20provide%20opportunities%20to%20secondary%20stage%20students%20to%20mainly%20build%20their%20capacity%20on%20ICT%20skills%20and%20make%20them%20learn%20through%20the%20computer-aided%20learning%20process.%20She%20proudly%20states%20that%20her%20students%20are%20now%20able%20to%20use%20computers%20proficiently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20living%20in%20an%20era%20of%20globalisation.%20To%20be%20a%20global%20citizen%2C%20digital%20education%20is%20a%20must.%20I%20want%20my%20students%20to%20know%20how%20to%20operate%20computers%20well%20and%20therefore%2C%20am%20exposing%20them%20to%20the%20technology%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20headmistress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGiving%20holistic%20education%20a%20must%20for%20this%20school%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESmt.%20Archana%20Nooguri%2C%20a%20National%20Awardee%20Teacher%202023%20from%20Telangana%2C%20works%20on%20improving%20enrolment%20rates%20%26amp%3B%20reducing%20dropouts.%20She%20develops%20low-cost%20teaching-learning%20material.%20She%20involved%20the%20community%20in%20setting%20up%20water%20purification%20plant%2C%20libra