2%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329929%2Farchana-nooguri-headmistress-government-school-national-teachers-award-enrollment-dropout%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2239-Year-Old%20Man%20Latest%20To%20Test%20Positive%20For%20Nipah%2C%20Total%206%20Cases%20In%20Kerala%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2039-year-old%20man%20in%20Kerala's%20Kozhikode%20district%2C%20who%20had%20sought%20treatment%20at%20a%20private%20hospital%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnipah-virus-explained-what-is-nipah-virus-its-previous-outbreaks-and-how-it-is-treated-4388980%5C%22%3ENipah%20virus%3C%2Fa%3E-affected%20were%20treated%20for%20other%20ailments%20earlier%2C%20has%20tested%20positive%20for%20the%20virus%2C%20taking%20the%20total%20known%20Nipah%20infections%20in%20the%20southern%20state%20to%20six.%20The%20zoonotic%20virus%2C%20transmitted%20between%20species%20from%20animals%20to%20humans%2C%20has%20already%20killed%20two%20people%20in%20Kerala%20this%20year%2C%20in%20its%20fourth%20outbreak%20since%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EState%20Health%20Minister%20Veena%20George's%20office%20on%20Friday%20said%20that%20the%2039-year-old%20man%20has%20been%20confirmed%20with%20the%20Nipah%20virus%20after%20his%20samples%20turned%20positive.%20He%20was%20under%20observation%20in%20a%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20virus%20strain%20seen%20in%20the%20state%20was%20the%20Bangladesh%20variant%2C%20which%20originated%205%20km%20from%20the%20forest%2C%20spreads%20from%20human%20to%20human%20and%20has%20a%20high%20mortality%20rate%2C%20though%20it%20is%20less%20infectious%2C%20the%20government%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20(ICMR)%20has%20sent%20monoclonal%20antibody%2C%20required%20to%20treat%20the%20Nipah%20virus%20infection%2C%20to%20Kerala.%20The%20medicine%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20clinically%20proven%2C%20but%20is%20the%20only%20available%20antiviral%20t