cines%20to%20prevent%20or%20cure%20the%20infection%2C%20which%20has%20a%20mortality%20rate%20of%20between%20about%2070%20per%20cent.%20The%20usual%20treatment%20is%20to%20provide%20supportive%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInfected%20people%20initially%20develop%20symptoms%20that%20include%20fever%2C%20respiratory%20distress%2C%20headaches%2C%20and%20vomiting%2C%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%20(WHO)%20says.%20Encephalitis%20and%20seizures%20can%20also%20occur%20in%20severe%20cases%2C%20leading%20to%20coma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20an%20outbreak%20in%20Kerala%20claimed%2021%20lives%2C%20with%20other%20outbreaks%20in%202019%20and%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694755320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F3p200kdg_nipah-virus_625x300_14_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkerala-news%2Fnipah-virus-latest-kerala-nipah-virus-detected-in-39-year-old-man-total-6-cases-in-kerala-now-4391609%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2039-year-old%20who%20had%20visited%20a%20Kerala%20hospital%20where%20a%20Nipah%20virus%20patient%20was%20treated%20has%20been%20infected%2C%20taking%20the%20total%20known%20infections%20in%20the%20southern%20state%20to%20six.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkerala-news%2Fnipah-virus-latest-kerala-nipah-virus-detected-in-39-year-old-man-total-6-cases-in-kerala-now-4391609%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkerala-news%2Fnipah-virus-latest-kerala-nipah-virus-detected-in-39-year-old-man-total-6-cases-in-kerala-now-4391609%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkerala-news%2Fnipah-virus-latest-kerala-nipah-virus-detected-in-39-year-old-man-total-6-cases-in-kerala-now-4391609%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mystery%20over%20China%20defense%20minister%20raises%20more%20questions%20for%20Xi%20Jinping%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22