Url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffood%2Ffood-workers-in-california-may-get-20-an-hour-minimum-wage-reports-4389315%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%206%20Needed%20From%202%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20Pull%20Off%20A%20Thriller%20Against%20Pakistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20finest%20cricketing%20contests%20of%20the%20Asia%20Cup%202023%20unfolded%20on%20Thrusday%20day%20as%20Sri%20Lanka%20edged%20Pakistan%20in%20a%20last-ball%20thriller%20to%20enter%20the%20final%20of%20the%20tournament.%20It%20was%20Sri%20Lanka's%20Kusal%20Mendis%20produced%20an%20outstanding%2091%20while%20Charith%20Asalanka%20gave%20him%20good%20company%20with%20a%20gutsy%20unbeaten%2049%20to%20set%20up%20the%20final%20against%20India.%20Pakistan%20looked%20to%20have%20done%20well%20to%20pull%20themsleves%20in%20the%20winning%20position%20after%20Shaheen%20Afridi's%20spectacular%20penultimate%20over.%20but%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%20reached%20the%20target%20of%20252%20runs%2C%20scoring%206%20runs%20from%20the%20last%202%20balls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHalf-centuries%20from%20Abdullah%20Shafique%20(52)%20and%20Mohammad%20Rizwan%20(86%20not%20out)%20had%20led%20Pakistan%20to%20a%20competitive%20252%20for%207%20off%2042%20overs%20after%20electing%20to%20bat%20on%20another%20rain-affected%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Sri%20Lanka%20replied%20in%20kind%20through%20Mendis%20and%20Asalanka%20as%20they%20inched%20past%20the%20target%20off%20the%20last%20ball%20of%20the%20match%2C%20also%20spoiling%20the%20possibility%20of%20an%20Indo-Pak%20summit%20clash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Kusal%20Perera%20departed%20early%2C%20Mendis%20in%20the%20company%20of%20Pathum%20Nissanka%20(29)%20steadied%20the%20Lankan%20innings%20with%20a%2057-run%20stand%20for%20the%20second%20wicket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20an%20even%20better%20passage%20was%20in%20the%20waiting%20for%20the%20Lankans%2C%20despite%20Nissanka%20spooning%20a%20return%20catch%20to%20Shadab%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMendis%20and%20Sadeera%20Samarawickrama%20(48%20off%2051%20balls)%20added%20100%20runs%20for%20the%20third%20wicket%2C%20as%20Lanka%20gradually%20bridged%20the%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMendis%20is%20blessed%20with%20natural%20striking%20prowess%20and%20timing%2C%20and%20his%20knock%20was%20a%20validation%20of%20that.%20The%20right-hander%20used%20his%20feet%20well%20against%20spinners%2C%20and%20faced%20the%20quicker%20lot%20with%20assurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESamarawickrama%2C%20even%20though%20he%20was%20pinged%20on%20the%20helmet%20once%20by%20Shaheen%20Afridi%2C%20kept%20his%20end%20going%20with%20some%20sensible%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20momentary%20rush%20ended%20his%20stay.%20Iftikhar%20caught%20him%20in%20no-man's%20land%20with%20a%20slightly%20fuller%20length%20ball%2C%20and%20Rizwan%20made%20an%20easy%20stumping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMendis%20milked%20a%20further%2033%20runs%20along%20with%20Asalanka%2C%20but%20Iftikhar%20returned%20to%20dismiss%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMendis'%20effort%20to%20turn%20the%20ball%20off%20his%20pads%20resulted%20in%20a%20leading%20edge%2C%20which%20was%20caught%20superbly%20by%20a%20diving%20Mohamamd%20Harris.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThereafter%20Sri%20Lanka%20fell%20into%20panic%20mode%2C%20losing%20four%20wickets%20in%20as%20many%20overs%20and%20it%20seemed%20that%20they%20were%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20botching%20up%20the%20chase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22zxx%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FsTYOFFQzml%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FsTYOFFQzml%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Nihari%20Korma%20(%40NihariVsKorma)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNihariVsKorma%2Fstatus%2F1702411519646937145%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2014%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EAfridi%20did%20the%20damage%20during%20that%20phase%20with%20two%20wickets%20in%20successive%20balls.%20But%20Asalanka%20held%20his%20nerves%20in%20the%20final%20over%20to%20carr