r%20tanks%20in%20neighboring%20states%20before%20coming%20to%20Rajasthan.%20They%20also%20argue%20that%20the%20high%20VAT%20is%20making%20fuel%20unaffordable%20for%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20association%20held%20a%20brief%2C%20symbolic%20strike%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20Thursday%20to%20urge%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%20to%20equalize%20VAT%20on%20petrol%20and%20diesel%2C%20as%20is%20the%20case%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20executive%20meeting%20of%20the%20association%20was%20held%20on%20Thursday%20evening.%20In%20this%2C%20the%20association%20unanimously%20decided%20to%20hold%20a%20statewide%20indefinite%20strike%20from%206%20am%20on%20September%2015%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20RPDA%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPetrol%20in%20Ganganagar%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%20112%20per%20litre%2C%20while%20diesel%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%2097.58%20per%20litre.%20Rajasthan%20has%20a%20total%20of%206%2C712%20petrol%20pumps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20RPDYA%20has%20called%20on%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%20to%20reduce%20the%20VAT%20on%20petrol%20and%20diesel%20to%20match%20that%20of%20neighboring%20states.%20If%20the%20government%20does%20not%20comply%2C%20the%20RPDYA%20has%20warned%20that%20it%20will%20continue%20the%20strike%20indefinitely.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694748480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fbtlls3bo_rajasthan-petrol-pump-strike-_625x300_15_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpetrol-pumps-in-rajasthan-begin-indefinite-strike-demanding-tax-reduction-4391463%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Petrol%20filling%20stations%20across%20Rajasthan%2C%20barring%20privately-owned%20and%20operated%20pumps%2C%20began%20an%20indefinite%20strike%20from%206%20am%20today%2C%20demanding%20a%20reduction%20in%20Value-Added%20Tax%20(VAT)%20on%20petrol%20and%20diesel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2F