20Goyal%2C%20in%20his%20response%20to%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20question%20by%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MP%20Pallabh%20Lochan%20Das%2C%20lists%20Pride%20East%20Entertainments%20Pvt.%20Ltd%20as%20one%20of%20the%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20PM%20Kisan%20Sampada%20Yojana.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20response%20by%20Goyal%2C%20dated%20March%2022%2C%202023%2C%20lists%20several%20such%20companies%20as%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20scheme%2C%20one%20of%20which%20is%20Pride%20East%20Entertainments%20Pvt.%20Ltd%2C%20which%20is%20claimed%20to%20have%20received%20a%20grant%20of%20Rs%2010%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOut%20of%20respect%20I%20will%20offer%20my%20free%20advice%20to%20the%20company%20linked%20to%20Assam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20which%20has%20received%20approval%20for%20a%20Rs%2010%20crore%20grant%20from%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%20Please%20make%20Union%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20and%20BJP%20MP%20Pallab%20Das%20a%20party%20to%20the%20case.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F6O3oJ7wKz2%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F6O3oJ7wKz2%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%20(%40GauravGogoiAsm)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGauravGogoiAsm%2Fstatus%2F1702290065651900488%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2014%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20have%20thrown%20Sarma%20into%20yet%20another%20controversy%20surrounding%20allegations%20of%20corruption.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20CrossCurrent%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20an%20Assam-based%20news%20website%2C%20had%20earlier%20reported%20that%20Pride%20East%20Entertainments%20Pvt.%20Ltd%2C%20owned%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20family%2C%20including%20his%20wife%20Riniki%20Bhuyan%20Sarma%2C%20his%20mother%20Mrinalini%20Devi%2C%20his%20son%20Nandil%20Biswa%20Sarma%2C%20and%20his%20daughter%20Sukanya%20Sarma%2C%20had%20purchased%2056%20bighas%20of%20agricultural%20land%20in%20February%202022%2C%2054%20bighas%20of%20which%20was%20meant%20only%20for%20agricultural%20use.%20However%2C%20the%20land%20was%20reclassified%20in%20April%202022%20as%20%E2%80%9Cindustrial%E2%80%9D%2C%20allowing%20Pride%20East%20Entertainments%20Pvt.%20Ltd%20to%20propose%20a%20food%20processing%20plant%20at%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%20story%20broke%2C%20the%20Assam%20Congress%20has%20been%20demanding%20a%20detailed%20clarification%20from%20the%20chief%20minister%20in%20the%20state%20assembly.%20Gogoi%20alleged%20that%20Sarma%20has%20remained%20absent%20from%20the%20assembly%20to%20avoid%20a%20clarification%20on%20the%20matter%2C%20and%20that%20mere%20%E2%80%9Cdenial%E2%80%9D%20will%20not%20clear%20the%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20Gogoi%20published%20Goyal%E2%80%99s%20response%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20Sarma%20claimed%20that%20he%20would%20retire%20from%20public%20life%20if%20these%20allegations%20are%20proven%20to%20be%20true%20and%20maintained%20that%20the%20company%20owned%20by%20his%20family%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20received%20any%20grant%20from%20the%20Union%20government.%20His%20defence%2C%20however%2C%20appears%20to%20hinge%20on%20the%20assumption%20that%20either%20the%20Union%20government%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20released%20the%20grant%20or%20the%20company%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20received%20it.%20He%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20company%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20sought%20or%20claimed%20any%20subsidy%20from%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20reply%20itself%20clarifies%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20not%20released%20any%20funds%20to%20the%20mentioned%20company.%20I%20want%20to%20emphasize%20once%20again%20that%20neither%20my%20wife%20nor%20the%20company%20she%20is%20associated%20with%20has%20received%20or%20claimed%20any%20amount%20from%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%20If%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F70zQ1DGHTe%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F70zQ1DGHTe%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20(%40himantabiswa)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhimantabiswa%2Fstatus%2F1702228522327298087%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2014%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20leaders%20and%20news%20reports%2C%20however%2C%20have%20cited%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20documents%20to%20claim%20that%20Pride%20East%20Entertainments%20Pvt.%20Ltd%20is%20a%20beneficiary%20of%20a%20central%20scheme.%20Against%20this%20backdrop%2C%20Sarma%E2%80%99s%20response%20leaves%20a%20lot%20to%20be%20desired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Sarma%E2%80%99s%20wife%2C%20Riniki%20Bhuyan%20Sarma%2C%20released%20a%20statement%20that%20merely%20reiterated%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20(Pride%20East%20Entertainments%20Pvt.%20Ltd)%20is%20a%20law-abiding%20company%20with%20all%20its%20financial%20records%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%20With%20a%20long%20and%20successful%20business%20track%20record%2C%20PrideEast%20Entertainments%20Pvt%20Ltd.%2C%20like%20any%20other%20qualifying%20enterprise%2C%20is%20eligible%20to%20participate%20in%20government-supported%20programmes%2Fincentive%20schemes.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20present%20case%2C%20pertaining%20to%20the%20PM%20Kisan%20Sampada%20Scheme%2C%20PrideEast%20Entertainments%20has%20neither%20claimed%20nor%20received%20a%20single%20paisa%20of%20government%20subsidy%2C%20despite%20meeting%20all%20eligibility%20criteria%2C%E2%80%9D%20her%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20nothing%20but%20an%20attack%20to%20malign%20and%20defame%20a%2017-year-old%20Assamese%20enterprise%2C%20which%20has%20adhered%20to%20every%20aspect%20of%20the%20law%2C%20headed%20by%20a%20w