n%20the%20past.%20He%20was%20also%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Sheila%20Dikshit%20government%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20appointed%20the%20Delhi%20Congress%20chief%20on%20August%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELovely%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20Delhi%20unit%20will%20follow%20the%20party%20high%20command%20on%20any%20seat-sharing%20arrangements%20within%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20but%20will%20not%20%E2%80%9Ccompromise%20on%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20interests%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDelhi%20was%20the%20greenest%20capital%20in%20the%20world%20and%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20green%20cover%20was%20talked%20about%20everywhere.%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20ministers%20were%20called%20to%20even%20cities%20such%20as%20Copenhagen%20to%20discuss%20how%20Delhi%20was%20made%20the%20greenest%20capital.%20But%20in%20seven%20years%2C%20Delhi%20has%20gone%20from%20the%20greenest%20capital%20to%20become%20the%20most%20polluted%20capital.%20Both%20these%20parties%20are%20responsible%20for%20that.%20So%2C%20how%20can%20I%20stop%20myself%20from%20speaking%20against%20both%20of%20them%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhenever%20there%20will%20be%20an%20issue%20pertaining%20to%20development%20and%20welfare%20of%20Delhi%20we%20will%20speak%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELovely%20was%20speaking%20at%20an%20event%20at%20the%20Delhi%20Congress%20headquarters%20in%20Rouse%20Avenue.%20Several%20top%20Delhi%20Congress%20leaders%2C%20including%20Ajay%20Maken%2C%20Alka%20Lamba%2C%20Sandeep%20Dikshit%2C%20Pawan%20Khera%2C%20Udit%20Raj%2C%20among%20others%2C%20were%20present%20at%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20came%20just%20a%20day%20after%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20of%2026%20opposition%20parties%20on%20Wednesday%20(September%2013)%20at%20their%20first%20coordination%20committee%20meeting%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-alliance-to-boycott-tv-shows-that-conduct-inflammatory-debates%5C%22%3Econclude%20seat-sharing%20talks%20at%20the%20earliest.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelhi%20has%20seen%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Famid-disagreements-over-state-polls-congress-and-aap-say-india-alliance-is-for-national-election%5C%22%3E%20disagreements%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20members%20%E2%80%93%20AAP%20and%20the%20Congress%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMurmurs%20of%20fissures%20emerged%20after%20Delhi%20Congress%20leader%20Alka%20Lamba%20said%20on%20August%2016%2C%20after%20a%20party%20organisational%20meeting%2C%20that%20the%20Congress%20would%20contest%20all%20seven%20seats%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20in%20the%202024%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20drew%20sharp%20reactions%20from%20AAP%2C%20and%20there%20were%20speculations%20over%20whether%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20and%20AAP%E2%80%99s%20national%20convener%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20would%20attend%20the%20India%20bloc%E2%80%99s%20Mumbai%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20clarifications%20were%20issued%2C%20Kejriwal%20announced%20that%20he%20will%20attend%20the%20grouping%E2%80%99s%20third%20meeting%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Famid-disagreements-over-state-polls-congress-and-aap-say-india-alliance-is-for-national-election%5C%22%3EAmid%20Disagreements%20Over%20State%20Polls%2C%20Congress%20and%20AAP%20Say%20India%20Alliance%20Is%20for%20%E2%80%98National%E2%80%99%20Election%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20that%2C%20AAP%20had%20only%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fahead-of-second-opposition-meet-delhi-ordinance-issue-still-divides-aap-and-congress%5C%22%3Ejoined%20the%20second%20INDIA%20bloc%20meeting%20in%20Bengaluru%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20July%2C%20after%20the%20Congress%20publicly%20promised%20to%20not%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fahead-of-second-opposition-meet-congress-says-it-will-not-support-delhi-ordinance%5C%22%3Esupport%20the%20contentious%20Delhi%20ordinance%20on%20control%20of%20services%20in%20parliament%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20became%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-services-bill-rajya-sabha-arvind-kejriwal-centre-ias-officer-amit-shah%5C%22%3Elaw%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rift%20between%20the%20two%20parties%20over%20the%20Delhi%20ordinance%20had%20also%20dominated%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpatna-amidst-aap-congress-sparring-16-opposition-parties-vow-to-unitedly-fight-the-bjp%5C%22%3Efirst%20INDIA%20alliance%20meeting%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELovely%20said%20that%20as%20the%20new%20Delhi%20Congress%20president%2C%20his%20role%20is%20not%20to%20work%20with%20other%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20role%20is%20not%20to%20work%20with%20other%20parties%2C%20my%20role%20is%20to%20strengthen%20the%20Congress%20organisation.%20That%20(working%20with%20other%20parties)%20is%20the%20role%20of%20the%20leadership%20and%20whatever%20their%20direction%20will%20be%20we%20will%20follow.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20statements%20made%20by%20Lamba%20and%20the%20ensuing%20differences%20with%20AAP%2C%20Lovely%20said%20that%20he%20stands%20by%20the%20leaders%20who%20aired%20their%20views%20freely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20basic%20difference%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20parties%20is%20that%20we%20are%20allowed%20to%20express%20our%20views%20freely.%20Everyone%20can%20express%20their%20views%20freely%20and%20I%20stand%20by%20those%20leaders%20as%20they%20have%20every%20right%20to%20speak%20freely.%20The%20Congress%20is%20a%20disciplined%20party%2C%20and%20when%20the%20high%20command%20asked%20for%20our%20views%2C%20some%20were%20in%20support%20of%20it%20and%20some%20were%20against.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20everyone%20said%20that%20these%20are%20our%20views%20and%20whatever%20decision%20the%20high%20command%20takes%2C%20we%20will%20abide%20by%20that.%20So%2C%20there%20are%20no%20issues%20and%20the%20decisions%20(related%20to%20seat%20sharing)%20will%20be%20taken%20by%20the%20high%20command.%20But%20my%20duty%20as%20Delhi%20Congress%20chief%20is%20to%20strengthen%20the%20Congress%20and%20make%20the%20Delhi%20Congress%20ready%20for%20any%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20Lovely%E2%80%99s%20second%20run%20as%20the%20Delhi%20Congress%20president.%20He%20was%20asked%20to%20step%20down%20from%20his%20post%20in%202015.%20In%20May%202017%2C%20he%20joined%20the%20BJP%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Farvinder-singh-lovely-returns-to-congress-says-he-was-misfit-in-bjp%2Fstory-3v9ICOMOC9J7rRVxUYB0fL.html%5C%22%3Ereturned%20to%20the%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20February%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20his%20decision%20to%20leave%20the%20party%20in%20his%20speech%20at%20the%20event%20earlier%2C%20Lovely%20said%20that%20he%20had%20made%20a%20mistake%20which%20he%20continues%20to%20regret%2C%20and%20urged%20those%20who%20have%20left%20the%20Congress%20to%20return%20to%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20appealed%20to%20those%20workers%20who%20have%20become%20annoyed%20with%20us%20to%20return%20because%20their%20DNA%20is%20%5Bof%20the%5D%20Congress%2C%20which%20means%20for%20generations%20they%20have%20been%20in%20the%20Congress%20%5Bparty%5D%20and%20they%20are%20now%20feeling%20suffocated%20in%20other%20parties%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20the%20fight%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20started%20is%20not%20only%20a%20fight%20to%20strengthen%20the%20Congress%2C%20it%20is%20a%20fight%20to%20save%20this%20nation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20of%20India%20have%20to%20decide%20whether%20they%20want%20to%20build%20the%20leadership%20of%20one%20leader%20or%20the%20nation.%20That%20is%20why%20I%E2%80%99ve%20appealed%20to%20all%20Congress%20leaders%20that%20come%20and%20join%20us%20in%20the%20fight%20to%20save%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694700032000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2FLovely_Rahul-Gandhi_PTI.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Faap-bjp-responsible-for-making-delhi-the-most-polluted-capital-congresss-arvinder-singh-lovely%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Delhi%20was%20the%20greenest%20capital%20in%20the%20world%20and%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20green%20cover%20was%20talked%20about%20everywhere.%20But%20in%20seven%20years%2C%20Delhi%20has%20gone%20from%20the%20greenest%20capital%20to%20become%20the%20most%20polluted%20capital%2C'%20said%20Lovely%2C%20who%20has%20assumed%20charge%20as%20the%20Delhi%20Congress%20chief.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Faap-bjp-responsible-for-making-delhi-the-most-polluted-capital-congresss-arvinder-singh-lovely%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22No%20Need%20for%20Carmakers%20to%20Make%20It%20Mandatory%20to%20Install%20Six%20Airbags%3A%20Nitin%20Gadkari%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19123303%2Fgadkari-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EMinister%20for%20Road%20Transport%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20September%2013%20said%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%20make%20it%20mandatory%20for%20carmakers%20to%20install%20six%20airbags%20in%20cars%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fnews%2Fsix-airbags-not-mandatory-now-gadkari%2Farticle67302660.ece%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EHindu%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EBusinessLine%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20policy%20was%20to%20come%20into%20effect%20from%20October%201.%20But%20the%20proposal%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20finalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20make%20it%20mandatory%E2%80%A6everyone%20%5Bcar%20companies%5D%20is%20doing%20it%2C%20and%20some%20of%20them%20are%20making%20advertisements%20and%20getting%20good%20share%20%5Bin%20sales%5D%2C%20and%20those%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20do%20it%2C%20they%20are%20pressing%20them%20%5Bcars%20with%206%20airbags%20in%20sales%5D%E2%80%A6if%20they%20want%20good%20sales%2C%20they%20have%20to%20make%20six%20airbags%2C%20and%20if%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20make%20it%2C%20it%20is%20their%20problem.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20make%20it%20mandatory%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Gadkari.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20has%20come%20as%20a%20relief%20for%20automakers%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20had%20opposed%20it%20saying%20it%20would%20increase%20costs%20and%20deter%20buyers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20former%20Tata%20Sons%20chairman%20Cyrus%20Mistry%20died%20in%20a%20car%20accident%20in%20September%202022%2C%20Gadkari%20had%20said%20that%20six%20airbags%20will%20soon%20become%20mandatory%20in%20all%20cars%2C%20adding%20that%20there%20is%20no%20question%20of%20compromising%20on%20international%20standard%20of%20road%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Gadkari%E2%80%99s%20announcement%2C%20road%20safety%20experts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fortuneindia.com%2Fenterprise%2Ftalks-with-govt-underway-on-6-airbags-3-point-seatbelts-maruti-suzuki%2F110225%5C%22%3Ehad%20flagged%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20in%20a%20country%20where%20wearing%20rear%20seat%20belts%20is%20unheard%2C%20mandating%20the%20installation%20of%20six%20airbags%20can%20be%20counterproductive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20six%20airbags%20in%20passenger%20vehicles%20should%20be%20made%20mandatory%20once%2085%25%20of%20the%20people%20start%20wearing%20rear%20seat%20belts.%20Once%20this%20figure%20is%20crossed%20pan-India%2C%20the%20government%20should%20go%20ahead%20with%20making%20this%20provision%20of%20six%20airbags%20mandatory%2C%E2%80%9D%20K.K.%20Kapila%2C%20president%20emeritus%2C%20International%20Road%20Federation%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fortuneindia.com%2Fenterprise%2Ftalks-with-govt-underway-on-6-airbags-3-point-seatbelts-maruti-suzuki%2F110225%5C%22%3Ehad%20told%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EFortune%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fnews%2Fsix-airbags-mandatory-for-smallest-of-cars-distance-between-tolls-to-be-60-km-gadkari%2Farticle65249779.ece%5C%22%3Ehad%20expressed%3C%2Fa%3E%20his%20determination%20to%20stand%20by%20his%20decision%2C%20despite%20the%20auto%20industry%E2%80%99s%20concerns%20about%20rising%20costs.%20He%20had%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20industry%20got%20upset%20because%20I%20made%20six%20airbags%20mandatory%20in%20economic%20models%E2%80%A6they%20said%20cost%20will%20increase%2C%20but%20I%20said%20let%20it%20increase%E2%80%A6if%20a%20porr%20man%20dies%2C%20let%20him%20die%2C%20and%20save%20the%20rich%20man%2C%20is%20it%3F%20So%20from%20now%20on%2C%20any%20economic%20model%2C%20the%20smallest%20of%20the%20smallest%2C%20even%20nano%20model%2C%20every%20car%20will%20have%20six%20airbags.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20clear%20why%20the%20government%20took%20a%20U-turn%2C%20not%20making%20the%20installation%20of%20six%20airbags%20mandatory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20leading%20car%20manufacturer%20told%20the%20business%20daily%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20most%20passenger%20cars%2C%20especially%20those%20priced%20Rs%208%20lakh%20and%20above%2C%20come%20with%20six%20airbags%20as%20standard%20now%2C%20and%20they%20will%20also%20do%20the%20same%20for%20future%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20safety%20point%20of%20view%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20features%20are%20getting%20added%2C%20and%20getting%20six%20airbags%20as%20standard%20has%20become%20a%20norm%20for%20us%20now.%20The%20passenger%20cars%20come%20with%20an%20occupant%20detection%20system%2C%20and%20also%20a%20three-point%20seatbelt%20for%20the%20middle%20passenger%20at%20the%20rear%20seat%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20senior%20official%20with%20a%20leading%20company%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20such%20as%20Hyundai%20Motor%20India%20recently%20launched%20its%20Exter%20small%20SUV%20with%20six%20airbags%20as%20standard%2C%20and%20its%20small%20car%20Grand%20i10%20Nios%20also%20comes%20with%20four%20airbags%20as%20standard%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20decisions%20assume%20significance%20in%20a%20country%20that%20has%20the%20deadliest%20roads%20in%20the%20world.%20Poor%20conditions%2C%20lax%20enforcement%2C%20unsafe%20vehicles%20and%20stray%20animals%20lead%20to%20more%20than%20900%2C000%20deaths%20and%20injuries%20a%20year%2C%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Ffeatures%2F2023-05-24%2Ffour-problems-and-solutions-for-india-s-dangerous-roads%5C%22%3Ereported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESafety%20audits%20of%20road%20designs%20before%20starting%20construction%20are%20%E2%80%9Cgrossly%20overlooked%E2%80%9D%20in%20India%2C%20S.%20Velmurugan%2C%20chief%20scientist%20of%20traffic%20engineering%20and%20safety%20at%20the%20Delhi-based%20Central%20Road%20Research%20Institute%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Ffeatures%2F2023-05-24%2Ffour-problems-and-solutions-for-india-s-dangerous-roads%5C%22%3Ehad%20told%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20May%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDevelopers%20rely%20on%20software%20for%20designing%20the%20streets%20without%20checking%20whether%20they%20meet%20the%20needs%20of%20all%20road%20users%20and%20ensuring%20there%20are%20no%20flaws%20on%20the%20ground.%20It%E2%80%99s%20possible%20to%20reduce%20fatalities%20by%20at%20least%2025%25%20if%20authorities%20do%20the%20design%20audit%2C%20Velmurugan%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20enforcement%20of%20speed%2C%20drunk%20driving%20and%20seat%20belt%20laws%20scores%20lower%20than%20China%20and%20the%20UK%2C%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%2C%20citing%20a%20World%20Health%20Organization%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20proposed%20a%20new%20Motor%20Vehicles%20Act%20with%20stricter%20safety%20regulations%20to%20deter%20offenders%2C%20but%20many%20states%20resisted%20its%20implementation%20and%20reduced%20the%20substantial%20penalties%20for%20violators%2C%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694698232000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19123303%2Fgadkari-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fno-need-for-carmakers-to-make-it-mandatory-to-install-six-airbags-nitin-gadkari%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20move%20has%20come%20as%20a%20relief%20for%20automakers%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20had%20opposed%20it%20saying%20it%20would%20increase%20costs%20and%20deter%20buyers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fno-need-for-carmakers-to-make-it-mandatory-to-install-six-airbags-nitin-gadkari%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Doc%20By%20Day%2C%20Wildlife%20Photographer%20Always%3A%2010%20Phenomenal%20Clicks%20By%20a%20Heart%20Surgeon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20conservation%20and%20respect%20for%20the%20wild%2C%20Padma%20Bhushan%20awardee%20Dr%20Ramakanta%20Panda%20and%20nature%20are%20on%20the%20same%20page.%20A%20major%20chunk%20of%20the%20heart%20surgeon%E2%80%99s%20day%20is%20spent%20tending%20to%20patients%20at%20the%20Asian%20Heart%20Institute%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20which%20he%20established%20in%202002.%20This%20leaves%20little%20time%20for%20other%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20whenever%20he%20does%20manage%20an%20escape%20from%20his%20busy%20schedule%2C%20he%20ventures%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326801%2Fvedhapriya-ganesan-snake-rescuer-wildlife-conservationist-pet-stylist-chennai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einto%20the%20wilderness%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20his%20camera%20and%20some%20food%20supplies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20life%20lessons%2C%20he%20says%2C%20that%20wildlife%20photography%20has%20taught%20him%20are%20patience%20(%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CI%20once%20waited%20for%20six%20hours%20over%20two%20days%20at%2045%20degrees%20Celsius%20to%20get%20a%20photograph%20of%20a%20tiger%20couple%20mating%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E)%20and%20honour%20for%20the%20subject%20%E2%80%94%20lessons%20that%20have%20stood%20him%20in%20good%20stead%20both%20in%20the%20wilderness%20and%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20photography%20journey%20is%20as%20compelling%20as%20his%20medical%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20trained%20under%20the%20renowned%20Dr%20Denton%20Cooley%20%E2%80%94%20famed%20for%20the%20first%20successful%20human%20heart%20transplant%20%E2%80%94%20whose%20interview%20he%20chanced%20upon%20in%20Class%209.%20Since%20then%2C%20matters%20of%20the%20heart%20held%20a%20fascination%20for%20him%20and%20there%20was%20no%20looking%20back.%20Despite%20a%20lucrative%20career%20at%20the%20Cleveland%20Clinic%2C%20in%201993%2C%20Dr%20Ramakanta%20returned%20to%20India%20in%20an%20attempt%20%E2%80%9Cto%20offer%20the%20kind%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329080%2Fmission-icu-provides-critical-healthcare-facilities-to-rural-indian-hospitals-through-kits%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvanced%20medical%20treatment%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%E2%80%99s%20taken%20for%20granted%20overseas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20would%20ask%20how%20pursuing%20a%20career%20in%20medicine%20allows%20time%20for%20hobbies%2C%20but%