%20chutney.%20Say%2C%20our%20beloved%20%3Cem%3Esamosa%20%3C%2Fem%3Efor%20example%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecan%20you%20imagine%20eating%20it%20without%20the%20tangy%20%3Cem%3Esauth%20%3C%2Fem%3E(sweet%20and%20sour)%20and%20%3Cem%3Ehari%20%3C%2Fem%3Echutney%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E(made%20out%20of%20green%20chillies)%3F%20Or%20say%20the%20dosa%20without%20the%20%3Cem%3Enariyal%20%3C%2Fem%3Echutney%20(made%20out%20of%20coconut)%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20its%20delicate%20appearance%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F276309%2Fbuy-homemade-pickle-on-amazon-best-indian-chutney-list%2F%5C%22%3Eprocess%20of%20crafting%20chutney%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecan%20be%20quite%20laborious.%20Leveraging%20India%E2%80%99s%20enduring%20affection%20for%20chutney%2C%20two%20childhood%20friends%20have%20successfully%20constructed%20an%20empire%20out%20of%20this%20flavourful%20condiment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20chutney%2C%20you%20may%20wonder%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Prasanna%20Natarajan%2C%20Co-Founder%20of%20Chutnefy%2C%20during%20a%20conversation%20with%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%9CQuite%20simply%20because%20Indians%20can%E2%80%99t%20do%20without%20chutneys.%20Our%20aim%20is%20to%20create%20a%20brand%20that%20offers%20all-natural%2C%20preservative-free%20options%2C%20making%20it%20more%20convenient%20for%20people%20to%20enjoy%20their%20beloved%20side%20dish.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20what%20makes%20their%20chutneys%20unique%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20because%20these%20blends%20are%20ready%20in%20just%205%20seconds.%20The%20brand%20offers%20an%20all-natural%2C%20preservative-free%20premix%20in%20which%20you%20simply%20need%20to%20add%20water%2C%20mix%20and%20presto%20%E2%80%94%20your%20chutney%20is%20ready%20to%20consume.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBringing%20chutneys%20to%20mainstream%20markets%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFounded%20by%20two%20school%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20Prasann