the%20country%2C%20including%20cities%20like%20Mumbai%2C%20Bangalore%20and%20Hyderabad.%20We%20also%20have%20been%20exporting%20to%20countries%20like%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20Singapore%2C%20United%20States%2C%20Canada%20and%20Germany%2C%E2%80%9D%20Prasanna%20informs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20is%20currently%20earning%20a%20revenue%20of%20around%20Rs%2050%20lakhs%20per%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20The%20Consumers%20Say%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESagar%20Mathu%2C%20who%20was%20born%20and%20raised%20in%20Chennai%20but%20moved%20to%20Mumbai%20for%20work%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20always%20loved%20our%20traditional%20south%20Indian%20chutneys%20and%20really%20missed%20them%20when%20I%20moved%20here.%20I%20came%20across%20this%20brand%20on%20Instagram%20and%20decided%20to%20give%20it%20a%20try.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20really%20love%20about%20them%20is%20that%20their%20chutneys%20do%20not%20feel%20like%20packed%20goods.%20It%20takes%20about%204-5%20seconds%20to%20make%20and%20look%20like%20they%20are%20homemade.%20The%20taste%20is%20authentic%20and%20feels%20straight%20out%20of%20my%20mother%E2%80%99s%20kitchen.%20I%20am%20a%20fitness%20enthusiast%20and%20their%20chutneys%20do%20not%20have%20sugar%20which%20is%20also%20why%20I%20love%20their%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCvBw0OfNSDU%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCvBw0OfNSDU%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%