9908%2Fcaro-water-india-first-eco-friendly-drinking-water-box-innovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewater%20cans%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20QR%20codes%20every%20month%20across%20Chennai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20you%20swig%20from%20a%20plastic%20can%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalachander%20is%20a%20graduate%20in%20environmental%20law%20from%20the%20National%20Law%20School%20of%20India%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20whereas%20Bharath%20is%20an%20electronics%20engineer%20by%20profession.%20After%20working%20with%20several%20companies%2C%20the%20Chennai-based%20brothers%20got%20together%20to%20work%20in%20the%20water%20space%20that%20is%20governed%20by%20unorganised%20players%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Balachander%20(46)%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20Chennai%2C%20people%20are%20dependent%20on%20water%20tanks%20for%20their%20daily%20water%20needs%20as%20the%20groundwater%20is%20very%20polluted%20or%20it%20is%20so%20saline%20that%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20use.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20day%2C%20more%20than%2025%20lakh%20cans%20of%2020-litre%20capacity%20are%20sold%20in%20Chennai.%20Even%20the%20poorest%20here%20are%20dependent%20on%20water%20cans%20that%20cost%20Rs%2035-45.%20But%20no%20one%20really%20knows%20the%20quality%20of%20water%20and%20of%20these%20cans.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20plastic%20water%20cans%20are%20also%20overused.%20You%20are%20not%20supposed%20to%20reuse%20these%20water%20cans%20beyond%20a%20certain%20extent%20after%20which%2C%20they%20start%20to%20lose%20their%20transparency.%20But%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20cans%20you%20see%20in%20the%20market%20will%20be%20completely%20clouded%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20happens%20due%20to%20the%20cans%20being%20left%20under%20the%20sun.%20The%20UV%20rays%20break%20the%20plastic%20into%20smaller%