ki%2C%20Jamal%20Saeed%20Abdul%20Rahim%2C%20Muhammad%20Abdullah%20Khalil%20Hussain%20arRahayyal%2C%20and%20Muhammad%20Ahmed%20al-Munawar%20were%20behind%20the%20act.%20Bhanot%20displayed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325596%2Fjournalist-pir-muhammed-munis-letter-to-gandhi-sparked-champaran-satyagraha-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremarkable%20courage%20%3C%2Fa%3Eas%20she%20saved%20the%20lives%20of%20more%20than%20350%20passengers%20on%20board.%20For%20her%20gallantry%2C%20she%20was%20posthumously%20awarded%20the%20Ashoka%20Chakra%20in%201987.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20such%20hero%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20aviation%20domain%20was%20Captain%20Durba%20Banerjee.%20As%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20woman%20pilot%2C%20it%20suffices%20to%20say%20she%20took%20India%20to%20the%20skies%20through%20her%20work.%20When%20she%20joined%20Indian%20Airlines%20in%201956%2C%20it%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20women%20across%20India%20to%20shatter%20glass%20ceilings%20and%20step%20into%20leadership%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20turned%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326955%2Frare-pics-of-milestones-and-historic-moments-of-india-music-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeaf%20ear%20to%20stereotypes%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20clouded%20her%20path%20as%20she%20persisted%20in%20her%20endeavours.%20Throughout%20her%20career%2C%20she%20accumulated%20an%20impressive%20flight%20time%20of%20over%209%2C000%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Neerja%20and%20Captain%20Banerjee%20made%20their%20mark%20in%20the%20skies%2C%20Mumbai-born%20Persis%20Khambatta%20made%20it%20in%20front%20of%20the%20camera.%20Her%20career%20was%20tinged%20with%20successes%2C%20the%20most%20popular%20one%20being%20her%20role%20of%20Lieutenant%20Ilia%20in%20Star%20Trek%3A%20The%20Motion%20Picture%20in%201979.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20daring%20Khambatta%20went%20bald%20for%20it.%20Through%20her%20work%2C%20she%20is%20credited%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296852%2Fpilot-freedom-fighter-odisha-chief-minister-biju-patnaik-incredible-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epaving%20the%20way%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20Indian%20actors%20in%20Hollywood.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Heroines%20of%20war%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Bangladesh%20Liberation%20War%20(1947%E2%80%931971)%2C%20a%20group%20of%20freedom%20fighters%20organised%20themselves%20into%20a%20group%20called%20the%20%E2%80%98Mukti%20Bahini%E2%80%99.%20They%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20young%20women%20to%20be%20trained%20in%20combat%20and%20various%20operations.%20Two%20of%20its%20members%20Captain%20Sitara%20Begum%20and%20Taramon%20Bibi%20were%20conferred%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98Bir%20Protik%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20the%20fourth%20highest%20gallantry%20award%20in%20Bangladesh%20%E2%80%94%20for%20their%20outstanding%20bravery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaramon%20Bibi%20worked%20as%20a%20cook%20for%20the%20Mukti%20Bahini%20and%20never%20missed%20a%20chance%20to%20use%20this%20position%20of%20hers%20to%20roam%20through%20the%20area%20and%20keep%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324744%2Fmany-nayak-historic-film-on-caste-kahi-debe-sandesh-created-chhatisgarhi-cinema%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrack%20of%20happenings.%3C%2Fa%3E%20She%20did%20this%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20a%20woman%20with%20a%20mental%20disability.%20She%20would%20observe%20the%20Pakistani%20Army%E2%80%99s%20movements%20and%20then%20report%20these%20to%20the%20Mukti%20Bahini%2C%20who%20would%20then%20act%20on%20these%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptain%20Sitara%20Begum%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20served%20as%20a%20doctor%20with%20the%20force.%20The%20Kolkata%20native%20oversaw%20operations%20at%20a%20Bangladesh%20Hospital%20where%20casualties%20of%20war%20and%20emergent%20cases%20needed%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYears%20before%20these%20two%20fearless%20women%20could%20play%20their%20role%2C%20a%20young%20girl%20Rajkumari%20Gupta%20displayed%20the%20same%20zeal%20during%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324194%2Fkishori-mohan-bandyopadhyay-worked-with-ronald-ross-malaria-research-nobel-prize-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20freedom%20struggle%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20and%20her%20husband%20Madan%20Mohan%20Gupta%20joined%20the%20Independence%20movement%20where%20they%20would%20deliver%20secret%20messages%20to%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENumerous%20times%2C%20Gupta%20put%20her%20life%20on%20the%20line%20while%20delivering%20guns%20to%20the%20revolutionaries.%20She%20once%20famously%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EHum%20upar%20se%20Gandhivaadi%20the%2C%20neeche%20se%20krantivaadi%20the%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(We%20were%20Gandhians%20from%20above%3B%20underneath%20we%20were%20revolutionaries).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Breaking%20stereotypes%20through%20literature%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20and%20their%20pragmatic%20approaches%20to%20dealing%20with%20crisis%20situations%20have%20gone%20down%20in%20history.%20For%20instance%2C%20Dr%20Gangubai%20Hangal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20it%20was%20taboo%20for%20women%20to%20take%20up%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F307227%2Fsitar-makers-of-miraj-handcraft-tanpura-veena-for-musicians-artisans-music-industry%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclassical%20music%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20not%20only%20did%20it%20but%20excelled%2C%20going%20on%20to%20win%20the%20Sangeet%20Natak%20Akademi%20Award%20(1973)%2C%20the%20Padma%20Bhushan%20(1971)%20and%20the%20Padma%20Vibhushan%20(2002).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20the%20chosen%20one%20to%20sing%20the%20welcome%20song%20at%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20session%20in%20Belagavi%20in%201924.%20The%20audience%20comprising%20Gandhi%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20Sarojini%20Naidu%2C%20and%20Maulana%20Abul%20Kalam%20Azad%20watched%20on%20admiringly.%20Hangal%20also%20performed%20at%20the%20Dover%20Lane%20Music%20Conference%20and%20the%20All%20Bengal%20Music%20Festival%20%E2%80%94%20two%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20prestigious%20classical%20music%20events%2C%20continuously%20for%2015%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20literary%20magic%20maker%20Subhadra%20Kumari%20Chauhan%20donned%20many%20hats.%20The%20Hindi%20poet%20was%20also%20a%20freedom%20fighter%20and%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F301563%2Fmusician-chiranjit-singh-invented-acid-house-genre-influenced-global-music-with-rd-burman%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebody%20of%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20includes%20nearly%20100%20poems%20and%2050%20short%20stories%20focused%20on%20caste%20discrimination%20and%20the%20dowry%20system.%20One%20of%20her%20well-known%20creations%20is%20the%20collection%20%E2%80%98Mukul%E2%80%99%20released%20in%201930%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20famous%20%E2%80%98Jhansi%20Ki%20Rani%E2%80%99%20poem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20after%20her%20marriage%20to%20Lakshman%20Singh%20Chauhan%20at%20the%20age%20of%2015%20that%20Subhadra%E2%80%99s%20political%20career%20took%20off.%20She%20refused%20to%20toe%20the%20line%20and%20abandoned%20the%20%3Cem%3Eghoonghat%20%3C%2Fem%3Edespite%20family%20objections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201921%2C%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20joined%20the%20Non-Cooperation%20Movement%20and%20led%20the%20%E2%80%98Jhanda%20Satyagraha%E2%80%99%20in%20Jabalpur%2C%20raising%20the%20In